NK010(tha)004:0: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje phur pa rgyud lugs kyi
NK010(tha)004:1: sgrub thabs rdo rje khros pa'i bcud dum dpag bsam
NK010(tha)004:2: ljon pa zhes bya ba bzhugs /
NK010(tha)004:3: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen rdo rje phur pa'i sgrub
NK010(tha)004:4: thabs rdo rje khros pa'i bcud dum dpag bsam ljon
NK010(tha)004:6: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi phrin las kyi bdag nyid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)004:7: rgyal kun bde gshegs snying po'i rang bzhin ni //
NK010(tha)004:8: stong nyid snying rje'i nyams su rol pa'i gar //
NK010(tha)004:9: sku gsum yan lag bdun ldan phur bu'i dngos //
NK010(tha)004:10: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi phyag rgyas mtshon la 'dud //
NK010(tha)004:11: gang zhig phur pa sgrub pa'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK010(tha)004:12: thabs las mkhas mchog rig 'dzin sde snod che'i //
NK010(tha)004:13: zab don bskyed rdzogs rgyud lung yongs 'du ba'i //
NK010(tha)004:14: phrin las dpag bsam ljon pa 'dir bsnyen cig /
NK010(tha)004:15: de la rdo rjee theg pa'i lam gyi 'jug sgo
NK010(tha)004:16: ma nor ba'i dkyil 'khor du rdo rje slob dpon
NK010(tha)004:17: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa las dbang thob nas dngos
NK010(tha)004:18: grub kyi brten gzhi sdom pa dang dam tshig la
NK010(tha)004:19: gnas pa / rim pa dang po lha'i rnal 'byor
NK010(tha)004:20: la sogs te dbang bzhi'i lam gyis dag bya dag
NK010(tha)004:21: 'bras las sngags lam gyi rgyu 'bras zab mo bskyed
NK010(tha)004:22: rdzogs zung 'jug gi go don rnyed cing dad brtson
NK010(tha)004:23: dang byang chub sems gnyis ldan pa'i sgrub pa pos
NK010(tha)004:24: nyams su blang ba yin te /
NK010(tha)004:25: rdo rje khros pa'i rtsa rgyud las /
NK010(tha)004:26: bde bar gshegs pa kun gyi gtso //
NK010(tha)004:27: yab yum sras bcas snang ba yang //
NK010(tha)004:28: byang chub sems kyi ngo bor gcig /
NK010(tha)004:30: mnyan bsam bsgom pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK010(tha)004:31: blo yi rtog pa kha phye nas //
NK010(tha)004:32: nges pa'i don 'di rtogs par gyis //
NK010(tha)004:33: nges pa'i don 'di ma rtogs na //
NK010(tha)004:34: bsgom dang bsgrub pa yun ring kyang //
NK010(tha)004:37: de la sbyor dngos rjes gsum las /
NK010(tha)004:39: dang po gnas kyi mtshan nyid dang /
NK010(tha)004:42: rgyan dang mchod rdzas dkram pa la sogs sgrub khog tu shes par bya'o //
NK010(tha)004:43: gnyis pa rnam grangs bcu las /
NK010(tha)004:45: theg pa chen po'i gang zag tu blo ma bcos
NK010(tha)004:46: na gsang sngags kyi gzugs brnyan du 'khyams pas tshad
NK010(tha)004:47: med bzhi bsgom par bya ste /
NK010(tha)004:49: gang rnams sdug bsngal nyen pa las //
NK010(tha)004:50: bral bar 'dod pa snying rje yin //
NK010(tha)004:51: byams pa phan pa bsgrub pa ste //
NK010(tha)004:52: kun la skyobs shing phan par dga' //
NK010(tha)004:53: rab tu dga' ba dga' ba ste //
NK010(tha)004:54: dam pa'i don la bdun pa'o //
NK010(tha)004:55: chags sdang gnyis dang bral ba ni //
NK010(tha)004:56: bar ma'i sems dang ldan pa ste //
NK010(tha)004:57: don dam pa yi btang snyoms bsgom //
NK010(tha)004:59: gnyis pa skyabs sems dang 'brel ba'i bdun rnam dag ni /
NK010(tha)004:60: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi rgyal
NK010(tha)004:61: ba sras dang bcas pa thams cad rdo rje gzhon
NK010(tha)004:62: nu'i dkyil 'khor gyi rol pa nyag gcig tu sad
NK010(tha)004:63: par byas pa la gzhan don du sangs rgyas bsgrub
NK010(tha)004:64: par dmigs pa'i dad gdung drag pos /
NK010(tha)004:65: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK010(tha)004:66: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)004:67: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK010(tha)004:68: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK010(tha)004:69: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK010(tha)004:70: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK010(tha)004:71: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK010(tha)004:72: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK010(tha)004:73: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK010(tha)004:74: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK010(tha)004:75: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK010(tha)004:76: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK010(tha)004:77: bde gshegs dbang phyug sems can la //
NK010(tha)004:78: dgos pa gsum phyir lus 'bul lo //
NK010(tha)004:79: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK010(tha)004:80: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK010(tha)004:82: dzahmh'u bam hohs rang la bstim pas rgyal thabs spyi blugs kyi dbang thob par bsam mo //
NK010(tha)004:83: gsum pa phyi rol pa bskrad pa ni /
NK010(tha)004:84: gtor ma 'bru gsum dang a k+aa ros brlabs pa byin nas /
NK010(tha)004:87: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK010(tha)004:88: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK010(tha)004:89: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK010(tha)004:90: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK010(tha)004:91: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK010(tha)004:92: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK010(tha)004:93: lus kyang dum bu stong du gtubs //
NK010(tha)004:94: snying yang tshal pa bdun du gtubs //
NK010(tha)004:98: bzhi pa mtshams bcad pa la bzhi las /
NK010(tha)004:99: dang po bskyed rim la khro bo 'chol ba'i mtshams ni /
NK010(tha)004:102: bsgrub pa'i ye shes tshon gang po //
NK010(tha)004:103: gsang ba'i sngags kyis bskyed nas kyang //
NK010(tha)004:104: sku dang ldan par rab bskyed cing //
NK010(tha)004:105: khams gsum khro bos gang bar mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:106: thugs las 'bar ba'i srog kyang zhugs //
NK010(tha)004:107: dbu la rdzogs pa'i rigs lngas bsrungs //
NK010(tha)004:108: nyi zla ri rab phur pas brgyan //
NK010(tha)004:109: khro bo mang pos gzir zhing mnan //
NK010(tha)004:110: sh+r+ai badz+ra ku m+aa ra sarba dush+tam ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h'u h'u h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:111: ces bskul bas khro bo'i tshogs kyis bgegs dang log
NK010(tha)004:112: par 'dren pa thams cad bsdigs shing brlagsa par bsam
NK010(tha)004:113: la / khro bcu so so'i stangs stabs dang phyag rgya bstun nas /
NK010(tha)004:116: mkha' dbus lag mthil sbyar te bsgreng //
NK010(tha)004:117: rkang pa brkyang bskum dor thabs 'dor //
NK010(tha)004:118: rdo rje'i stangs stabs gar nyid kyi //
NK010(tha)004:119: gom pa legs par 'jog byed pa //
NK010(tha)004:120: rdo rje h'u gi phyag rgya yin //
NK010(tha)004:121: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha h'u k+aa ra h'u /
NK010(tha)004:122: bar chad 'byung po gardza gardza h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:123: shes rab kyi ni rkang pa yis //
NK010(tha)004:124: thabs la rnam par 'khyud pas ni //
NK010(tha)004:125: lag gis rdo rje'i gar byed cing //
NK010(tha)004:126: rdo rje thal mo brdab pa ni //
NK010(tha)004:127: rnam par rgyal ba'i phyag rgya yin //
NK010(tha)004:128: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h+aum /
NK010(tha)004:129: bar chad 'byung po ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:130: las rnams kun la gsod par brtson //
NK010(tha)004:131: thabs kyi sbom po tha ma'i cha //
NK010(tha)004:132: de yi dbus gnas srid du brkyang //
NK010(tha)004:133: rdo rje dbyung pa'i phyag rgya yin //
NK010(tha)004:134: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha ni la dan+da h'u /
NK010(tha)004:135: bar chad 'byung po da ha da ha h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:136: g.yas pa nas ni phan tshun te //
NK010(tha)004:137: sor mo bsdus pas dbus gnas pa //
NK010(tha)004:138: kun tu bsdus pa brdeg pa'i stabs //
NK010(tha)004:139: gzhan ni yum gyi ngos bzhag ste //
NK010(tha)004:140: dbu ma'i tshad du 'gyings pa ste //
NK010(tha)004:141: dpa' bo rngams pa'i phyag rgya yin //
NK010(tha)004:142: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h'u /
NK010(tha)004:143: bar chad 'byung po pa tsa pa tsa h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:144: shes rab kyis ni bsgrub bya 'dzin //
NK010(tha)004:145: thabs kyis cod pan gdengs par byed //
NK010(tha)004:146: rnam par brtag pa chen po ni //
NK010(tha)004:147: mi g.yo rgyal po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK010(tha)004:148: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h'u /
NK010(tha)004:149: bar chad 'byung po b+han+d+ha b+han+d+ha h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:150: thal mo mnyam par sbyar nas ni //
NK010(tha)004:151: gung mos 'du byed bsgrub par bya //
NK010(tha)004:152: mthe bong dpral ba'i steng du bzhag /
NK010(tha)004:153: rta yi rgyal po gdengs pa'i rgya //
NK010(tha)004:154: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha h+ya gri wa h'u /
NK010(tha)004:155: bar chad 'byung po hu lu hu lu h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:156: ling+ga rting pas mnan nas kyang //
NK010(tha)004:157: lha chen rang bzhin 'dus par bya //
NK010(tha)004:158: thal mo mnyam gnas dbus su yang //
NK010(tha)004:159: gsang ba'i dbang po lta na'o //
NK010(tha)004:160: 'dod pa'i rgyal po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK010(tha)004:161: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha a pa ra tsi ta h'u /
NK010(tha)004:162: bar chad 'byung po tish+tha tish+tha h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:163: lag gnyis rdo rje dbus bstan te //
NK010(tha)004:164: rkang gnyis gshibs te drag tu mchong //
NK010(tha)004:165: 'jigs pa'i rang bzhin rnam brtags pa //
NK010(tha)004:166: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i phyag rgya yin //
NK010(tha)004:167: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h'u /
NK010(tha)004:168: bar chad 'byung po ts+tshin+d+ha ts+tshin+d+ha h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:169: nam mkha' rdo rje dbus gnas su //
NK010(tha)004:171: rdo rje 'jigs pa'i rgyan gyis bzhag /
NK010(tha)004:172: dpa' bo the tshom med pa'i rgya //
NK010(tha)004:173: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha tree lokya bi dza ya h'u /
NK010(tha)004:174: bar chad 'byung po b+hin+d+ha b+hin+d+ha h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:175: thur du rkang mthil mnyam gnas shing //
NK010(tha)004:176: lag pa so sor gar la brtson //
NK010(tha)004:177: stobs chen mchong ba'i nga rgyal ni //
NK010(tha)004:178: rdo rje stobs kyi phyag rgya yin //
NK010(tha)004:179: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa ba la h'u /
NK010(tha)004:180: bar chad 'byung po s+pho ta s+pho ta h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:181: de nas khro bo'i tshogs slar 'dus nas khro bo
NK010(tha)004:182: 'chol ba'i rang bzhin gyis rdo rje'i gur khang chen
NK010(tha)004:183: por gyur / gnyis pa 'byung ba gsum 'chol ba'i mtshams ni /
NK010(tha)004:185: khams gsum gdug pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)004:186: tsham rngams gzugs ni glog ltar 'bar //
NK010(tha)004:187: me rlung chu yis bsregs gtor bkrus //
NK010(tha)004:188: nyes byed gsum yang srid par grol //
NK010(tha)004:189: badz+ra dz+wa la ram ram yam kham /
NK010(tha)004:190: zhes brjod pas bskal pa'i me dpung /
NK010(tha)004:192: rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs 'khrugs pa'i ra ba gsum gyis
NK010(tha)004:193: phyogs kun gang bas mtshams bcad de cis kyang mi
NK010(tha)004:194: shigs par gyur / gsum pa phyag rgya mtshon cha 'chol ba'i mtshams ni /
NK010(tha)004:196: rdo rje rab tu k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)004:197: rab tu gsor zhing dril nas kyang //
NK010(tha)004:198: khams gsum 'khor ba bsgral nas ni //
NK010(tha)004:199: ye shes sku yis khyab gdal nas //
NK010(tha)004:200: 'dzin chags thams cad rnam par grol //
NK010(tha)004:202: khams gsum de bzhin rol pa'i sku //
NK010(tha)004:203: ma lus phur pas thebs zhes bya //
NK010(tha)004:204: gang zhig gnod pa'i tshogs rnams la //
NK010(tha)004:205: rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad nang //
NK010(tha)004:206: rdo rje phur pa mang shar zhing //
NK010(tha)004:207: de yis tshogs brgyad dag par bya //
NK010(tha)004:208: bdag dang gsum du ldan nas kyang //
NK010(tha)004:209: byang chub sems las rnam spros te //
NK010(tha)004:210: phung po rdul du bshigs nas kyang //
NK010(tha)004:211: sha khrag khams gsum gang bar dmigs //
NK010(tha)004:212: h'u gis rab tu nam mkha' gang //
NK010(tha)004:213: phata kyis rab tu gtor byas te //
NK010(tha)004:214: rdo rje ye shes tshon gang gis //
NK010(tha)004:215: khams gsum rab tu gang nas kyang //
NK010(tha)004:216: bsdus pas mtshon cha 'chol bar bsgom //
NK010(tha)004:217: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:218: ces brjod pas rdo rje dang phur bu gtso bor
NK010(tha)004:219: gyur pa'i mtshon cha 'chol ba'i gur khang chen pos
NK010(tha)004:221: bzhi pa bdag med lta ba'i mtshams ni /
NK010(tha)004:223: yum ni rnam par grol ba'i thugs //
NK010(tha)004:224: srid pa phur bur rtogs pa yis //
NK010(tha)004:225: srid pa gsum la thebs zhes bya //
NK010(tha)004:226: 'dzin dang rtog pa rnams spangs te //
NK010(tha)004:227: byang chub sems kyi gol sa bcad //
NK010(tha)004:228: bgegs zhes bya ba'i ming yang med //
NK010(tha)004:229: d+harma d+h+aa tu hoh lnga pa brda' sgo dbye ba ni /
NK010(tha)004:230: rdo rje bkod pa las phrad bsgyur ba /
NK010(tha)004:231: ma bcos spros pa med pa'i dkyil //
NK010(tha)004:232: skye med yongs la khyab pas 'khor //
NK010(tha)004:233: 'gyur med don rtogs mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK010(tha)004:234: phung po khams dang skye mched rnams //
NK010(tha)004:235: ye nas dbyer med rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK010(tha)004:236: de nyid ma rig ling tog ni //
NK010(tha)004:237: thugs rje'i thur mas dbye ru gsol //
NK010(tha)004:238: b+h+r+aum pra we sha ya phata /
NK010(tha)004:239: ces brjod pas mtshon pa tsam du dkyil 'khor gyi
NK010(tha)004:240: sgo bzhi lhag gis phye ste gzhal yas khang rten
NK010(tha)004:241: dang brten par bcas pa thal ler mthong bar bsam
NK010(tha)004:242: mo // drug pa brda' phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK010(tha)004:244: chos nyid ye nas phur pa la //
NK010(tha)004:245: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med de //
NK010(tha)004:246: gang du 'dzin pa smin pa'i rgyu //
NK010(tha)004:247: rgyu gcig 'bras bu bzang ngan gnyis //
NK010(tha)004:249: rtogs pa don gyi brda' phyag 'tshal //
NK010(tha)004:250: d+harma d+h+aa tu a k+aa ro y+aa mi na ma /
NK010(tha)004:251: zhes rnal ma'i don la blta'o //
NK010(tha)004:252: bdun pa bshags pa bya ba la rtogs pa lta ba /
NK010(tha)004:255: gdung ba smre sngags kyi sgo nas bshags pa'i rgyud
NK010(tha)004:256: chen bzhi las 'dir gsum pa ltar bshags pa la
NK010(tha)004:257: / bcas dang rang bzhin gyi kha na tho ba'i
NK010(tha)004:258: tshogs thams cad la stobs bzhi'i mtshan nyid dran pas
NK010(tha)004:260: ye shes lnga ldan bla ma rdo rje 'dzin //
NK010(tha)004:261: rdo rje rigs kyi lha tshogs dgongs su gsol //
NK010(tha)004:262: khrag 'thung khro bo khro mos byin gyis rlabs //
NK010(tha)004:263: bdag gi lus kyis srog gcod ma byin blangs //
NK010(tha)004:264: mi tshangs spyad cing ting 'dzin sku ma gsal //
NK010(tha)004:265: sku yi dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)004:266: +aah bdag gi ngag gis rdzun dang phra ma dang //
NK010(tha)004:267: ngag 'khyal tshig rtsub bzlas brjod grangs ma skyol //
NK010(tha)004:268: rdo rje bzlas pa'i don ni ma rtogs te //
NK010(tha)004:269: gsung gi dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)004:271: bdag gis snod ldan sems can thams cad la //
NK010(tha)004:272: brnab sems gnod sems log lta skyes pa dang //
NK010(tha)004:273: chos nyid zab mo'i don ni ma rtogs te //
NK010(tha)004:274: lta ba thugs kyi dam tshig nyams pa bshags //
NK010(tha)004:276: sems can thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas rgyur //
NK010(tha)004:277: ma rtogs bdag gis barngana dang skyon du bgrangs //
NK010(tha)004:278: sangs rgyas yon tan mtha' yas ma brjod cing //
NK010(tha)004:279: yon tan dam tshig nyams la mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)004:281: sangs rgyas phrin las sna tshogs dpag med kyis //
NK010(tha)004:282: snying rje chen pos sems can don ma byas //
NK010(tha)004:283: bdud rtsi lnga la longs spyod ma nus shing //
NK010(tha)004:284: phrin las dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)004:286: skye ba rnam bzhis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams //
NK010(tha)004:287: chos sku rnam dag dbyings las gzugs skur snang //
NK010(tha)004:288: bde ba chen pos kun la khyab dmigs te //
NK010(tha)004:289: yang dag don ma rtogs pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)004:290: zhes pas rgyud dag par bya'o //
NK010(tha)004:291: tshogs bsgrub la sogs pa'i tshe skabs 'dir rtags gdab
NK010(tha)004:292: par bya ste mched lcam rnams kyi sna rtse dang
NK010(tha)004:293: / mkhur mtshos gnyis su rak+ta'i thig le /
NK010(tha)004:294: spyi mgrin snying ga gsum du thal chen gyi tshom bu /
NK010(tha)004:296: snying gar zhag gi zo ris dang zla phyed rgya gram bris /
NK010(tha)004:297: de nas phan tshun gral phyag byas te 'dug go //
NK010(tha)004:298: brgyad pa byang chub sems dpa'i sngags kyi tshul khrims
NK010(tha)004:299: rnam par dag par bya ba'i phyir dam bca' ba
NK010(tha)004:300: ni / rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgya snying
NK010(tha)004:301: gar bcings te gzhan don la dmigs pa'i lhag bsam
NK010(tha)004:303: rnal 'byor dbang po ye shes mthar phyin pa //
NK010(tha)004:304: 'gro la phan mdzad thugs rjes dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK010(tha)004:305: srid pa gsum gyi gnyen rgyud gcig pu pa //
NK010(tha)004:306: lha yi lha khyod bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK010(tha)004:307: bde bar gshegs pa'i sprul pa rgya mtsho dang //
NK010(tha)004:308: rnal 'byor dbang phyug grub pa'i tshogs chen po //
NK010(tha)004:309: lha dang lha min sngags 'chang dam tshig can //
NK010(tha)004:310: kun nas 'dus pa rnams kyang dgongs su gsol //
NK010(tha)004:311: bdag ni rgyal srid mtho ris longs spyod dang //
NK010(tha)004:312: 'dod pa'i yon tan bdag bsgrub ma lags te //
NK010(tha)004:313: 'gro la snying brtse kho nas don brtson pa //
NK010(tha)004:314: 'di la kun mkhyen khyed ni dpang du gsol //
NK010(tha)004:315: mgon po ye shes sgrib pa mi mnga' bas //
NK010(tha)004:316: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK010(tha)004:317: 'phags mchog spyan sngar ji ltar dam bcas pa //
NK010(tha)004:318: sun par mi bgyi mgon khyod bslu ma lags //
NK010(tha)004:319: snying nas bdag ni khe dang grags la sogs //
NK010(tha)004:320: g.yo dang zang zing sems ni gtan spangs nas //
NK010(tha)004:321: gzhan don sgrub pa gcig po'i sems bzhag ste //
NK010(tha)004:322: rnal 'byor spyod pa chen po bdag gis spyad //
NK010(tha)004:323: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK010(tha)004:324: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK010(tha)004:325: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)004:326: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su gzung bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)004:327: srog chags thams cad gal te bdud gyur nas //
NK010(tha)004:328: dum bu stong du bdag gi lus gtubs kyang //
NK010(tha)004:329: byang chub sems mchog shes rab snying rje dang //
NK010(tha)004:330: yi dam rgyal ba khyod ni yongs mi spang //
NK010(tha)004:331: rdo rje'i dam tshig chen po rnams dang ni //
NK010(tha)004:332: rdo rje slob dpon rdo rje mched lcam dang //
NK010(tha)004:333: gzhan yang theg pa mchog la zhugs pa rnams //
NK010(tha)004:334: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong ci nus bsrungs //
NK010(tha)004:335: 'khor ba bdag med sgyu ma'i rang bzhin la //
NK010(tha)004:336: bdag ni 'jigs pa ci yang ma mchis te //
NK010(tha)004:337: ma rig skye bo rnams kyi don slad du //
NK010(tha)004:338: phyi mthar thug gi bar du gnas par spro //
NK010(tha)004:339: gzhan don 'khor ba rnams su spyod pa na //
NK010(tha)004:340: byang chub spyod pa rlabs chen bdag gis spyad //
NK010(tha)004:341: 'gro drug sems can rnams la phan gdags phyir //
NK010(tha)004:342: rang dbang du ni skye ba blang bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)004:343: bdag ni yongs su bzung ba'i 'jig rten nam //
NK010(tha)004:344: mya ngan 'das la spro ba ma mchis te //
NK010(tha)004:345: gang dang gang du sdug bsngal gnas rnams su //
NK010(tha)004:346: bskal pa rgya mtshor gnas shing phan par bgyi //
NK010(tha)004:347: srid par yun ring dus su brtson pa ni //
NK010(tha)004:348: byang chub sems dpa'i yi dam lags pas na //
NK010(tha)004:349: ji srid ngan song stongs par ma gyur pa //
NK010(tha)004:350: de srid bdag gis skyo ba'i sems mi bskyed //
NK010(tha)004:351: shes rab thabs kyis 'gro ba'i don bgyid pa //
NK010(tha)004:352: snying rje'i longs spyod de las ma mchis pas //
NK010(tha)004:353: sems dmyal yi dwags gshin rje'i 'jig rten yang //
NK010(tha)004:354: lha yi dga' tshal lta bur blta bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)004:355: 'gro la thugs rje dpal gyi mgur nas gsungs //
NK010(tha)004:356: rnal 'byor dam chos bdud rtsi mchog rnams ni //
NK010(tha)004:357: bdag gis 'jig rten thug pa ma mchis par //
NK010(tha)004:358: ji ltar 'tshams pa bzhin du rgyas par bgyi //
NK010(tha)004:359: srid par las dang rkyen gyi dbang gyur te //
NK010(tha)004:360: gang dang gang du dam chos 'jig pa der //
NK010(tha)004:361: me tshogs spu gri'i so yang brgal nas ni //
NK010(tha)004:362: phyi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos bzung //
NK010(tha)004:363: bla med byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de //
NK010(tha)004:364: sgrub pa mchog la zhugs pa'i skye bo la //
NK010(tha)004:365: tshe rabs rnams su mthu rtsal ci mchis kyis //
NK010(tha)004:366: skyes chen rnams kyi dgongs pa rtag tu bskang //
NK010(tha)004:367: dam pa'i chos dang sgrub pa'i gegs gyur pa //
NK010(tha)004:368: mi dang mi min gdug pa gang yang rung //
NK010(tha)004:369: bdag gis zhi dang khro bo'i phrin las kyis //
NK010(tha)004:370: yongs su zhi zhing rnam par gzhom par bgyi //
NK010(tha)004:371: rnal 'byor mchog gi theg chen bla med dang //
NK010(tha)004:372: rdo rje rgyal po khyod la brten nas ni //
NK010(tha)004:373: sangs rgyas zhing sbyong 'gro la sman slad du //
NK010(tha)004:374: byang chub snying po bdag gis rtogs par bgyi //
NK010(tha)004:375: bdag ni 'phags mchog phyag rgya mngon sprul te //
NK010(tha)004:376: gal te skabs med 'chi ba'i dus byung tshe //
NK010(tha)004:377: gsang sngags mgon po ye shes dkyil 'khor can //
NK010(tha)004:378: khyed kyi zhabs kyi drung du mchi bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)004:379: srid gsum sdug bsngal ci 'dra khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK010(tha)004:380: dmyal sogs med dpung zhi bar bgyid la sogs //
NK010(tha)004:381: sems can don la myur du bdag mchi na //
NK010(tha)004:382: dam pa rnams kyis nus mthu stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)004:383: dgu pa byin dbab pa ni /
NK010(tha)004:384: +amo badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes se gol bsnol mar gtogs pas /
NK010(tha)004:385: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa thams cad
NK010(tha)004:386: gsang sngags nang gi dkon mchog rtsa ba gsum gyi
NK010(tha)004:387: rnam par byon / b+ha ga w+aa na sa ma
NK010(tha)004:388: ya hoh zhes pas yab yum rnams kyi rjes chags
NK010(tha)004:389: rnam par byon / bskul / sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK010(tha)004:390: zhes pas stangs dpyal mnyam par rol /
NK010(tha)004:391: a la la hoh zhes pas sbyor mtshams nas byang
NK010(tha)004:392: chub kyi sems dngos grub kyi tshul du byung ba
NK010(tha)004:393: rang gi spyi gtsug tu thim /
NK010(tha)004:394: sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa dag /
NK010(tha)004:395: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs zhugs par bltas la /
NK010(tha)004:398: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)004:399: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)004:400: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)004:401: byin gyis rlob pa'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)004:402: dbang mchog bskur ba'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)004:403: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)004:405: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK010(tha)004:406: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK010(tha)004:407: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK010(tha)004:408: bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:409: h'u h'u h'u h'u gis byin bsdus pas /
NK010(tha)004:410: nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i lha tshogs rnams bdag dang gnas
NK010(tha)004:411: dang yo byad rnams la thim ste byin gyis brlabs
NK010(tha)004:412: par bsam mo // bcu pa mchod rdzas brlab pa la thun mong dang khyad par gnyis las /
NK010(tha)004:416: stong pa'i ngang las rang nyid yi dam du gsal
NK010(tha)004:417: ba'i thugs ka'i h'u las mchod rdzas so so'i ming
NK010(tha)004:418: yig dang po s+pha ra na phata kyis spros /
NK010(tha)004:420: sam ha ra na h'u gis 'khor 'das kyi dwangs bcud dang gnyis su med par bsdus /
NK010(tha)004:421: mchod rdzas rnams la thim pas lha mo bcu drug dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK010(tha)004:422: so so'i phyag rgya dang bcas /
NK010(tha)004:423: +amo sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe h'u /
NK010(tha)004:425: +aa lo ke h+r+aih g+han+d+he +aah l+aa s+ya h'u /
NK010(tha)004:427: g+airti h+r+aih n+airti +aah wi ni h'u /
NK010(tha)004:429: mri tam ke h+r+aih mu rany+dze +aah r+au pa h'u /
NK010(tha)004:431: r+aa sa h+r+aih d+harma d+h+aartu +aah rdo rje bdug spos
NK010(tha)004:432: ma la sogs pa re re la'ang grangs med par
NK010(tha)004:433: 'char bas nam mkha' gang bar gyur /
NK010(tha)004:434: gnyis pa khyad par ba ni rtsa rgyud las /
NK010(tha)004:435: pho thod mo thod ma ning thod //
NK010(tha)004:436: ba ling rak+ta bdud rtsir sbyar //
NK010(tha)004:437: zhes pas ma ning gi thod par gnas pa'i bdud rtsi /
NK010(tha)004:439: ram yam kham gis bdud rtsi'i dngos po bsregs gtor bkrus /
NK010(tha)004:440: stong pa'i ngang las rang gi thugs ka nas b+h+rum chad /
NK010(tha)004:441: bdud rtsi'i snod thod pa'i gzhal yas khang rdo rje'i
NK010(tha)004:442: rna ba can gyi nang du 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi
NK010(tha)004:443: pa'i lte bar mi sha dang byang sems dkar po
NK010(tha)004:444: la h'u m+aum / shar gyi rtsibs la ba lang gi sha dang dri chen la +amo l+aam /
NK010(tha)004:445: lhor khyi sha dang sha chen la s+w+aa m+aam /
NK010(tha)004:446: nub tu rta sha dang rak+ta la +aam p+aam /
NK010(tha)004:447: byang du glang po che'i sha dang dri chu la h+aa t+aam rnams kyis mtshan par gyur /
NK010(tha)004:448: s+pha ra na phata brjod pas rang gi snying ga'i h'u las 'od zer 'phros /
NK010(tha)004:449: sam ha ra na h'u gis zhing bcu'i sha dang
NK010(tha)004:450: 'khor 'das kyi bdud rtsi thams cad bsdus nas gdan
NK010(tha)004:451: dang bcas pa'i gsung yi ge'i 'khor lo la thim
NK010(tha)004:452: / de yongs su gyur pa las thugs kyi dkyil
NK010(tha)004:453: 'khor rigs so so'i phyag mtshan lngas yu ba byas
NK010(tha)004:455: de nyid kyang bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags las sku
NK010(tha)004:456: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor du gyur pa ni
NK010(tha)004:457: / h+aum m+aum las dbus su mi bskyod pa yab yum mthing ga /
NK010(tha)004:458: +amo l+aam las shar du rnam snang yab yum dkar po /
NK010(tha)004:459: s+w+aa m+aam las lhor rin 'byung yab yum ser po /
NK010(tha)004:460: +aam pam las nub tu snang mtha' yab yum dmar po /
NK010(tha)004:461: h+aa t+aam las byang du don grub yab yum ljang gu rnams su gyur /
NK010(tha)004:463: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa ko&a ham /
NK010(tha)004:464: a nu r+aa ga ya mi /
NK010(tha)004:465: dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes snyoms 'jug bde ba'i rol mos bskul /
NK010(tha)004:466: bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK010(tha)004:467: ces byang chub kyi sems yum gyi mkha' nang du spros pas sangs rgyas thams cad dgyes pa bskyed /
NK010(tha)004:468: sam ha ra na h'u zhes pas 'khor 'das kyi dwangs bcud dang lhan cig tshur 'dus /
NK010(tha)004:469: rigs lnga yab yum rjes chags kyi sbyor bas 'od
NK010(tha)004:470: du zhu ba las byung ba'i ye shes kyi bdud
NK010(tha)004:471: rtsi dam tshig gi bdud rtsi dang gnyis su med
NK010(tha)004:472: par gyur / zla ba'i kha gcod +amo dkar pos
NK010(tha)004:473: mtshan pa'i rdo rje rgya gram gyi lte bar h+r+aihdamara
NK010(tha)004:476: yongs su gyur pa las rta mgrin dmar po g.yas
NK010(tha)004:477: pad+ma dang g.yon rgya gram 'dzin pa'i lte ba man
NK010(tha)004:478: chad bdud rtsi'i nang du nub pa'i mdun nas bde
NK010(tha)004:482: rgyab nas za byed ma ste gsang ba'i yum bzhis
NK010(tha)004:483: 'khril zhing mnyam par sbyor ba'i sbyor mtshams nas ye
NK010(tha)004:484: shes kyi bdud rtsi'i rgyun babs pas dam tshig gi
NK010(tha)004:485: bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho dang ro gcig tu gyur par
NK010(tha)004:486: bsams la / g.yon pa'i mtheb srin bdud rtsi la gtad de /
NK010(tha)004:488: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aah zhes bargya'am nyer gcig gis mtha' brten pa bzlas mthar /
NK010(tha)004:489: rdo rjes g.yas skor du dkrug pa'i lbu ba la
NK010(tha)004:490: khro bo bdud rtsi'i 'khyil ba'i rdul phra rab 'phros
NK010(tha)004:492: mched lcam rnams la gtor bas mkhon gcugs byang bar 'gyur /
NK010(tha)004:493: h'u h'u h'u h'u h'u h+r+aih zhes brjod pas lha rnams bdud rtsi la thim par bsam mo //
NK010(tha)004:494: pho thod du gnas pa'i gtor ma bsang sbyangs /
NK010(tha)004:495: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum b+hany+dza ka p+aa la b+h+r+aum /
NK010(tha)004:496: dpa' bo thod pa'i gzhal yas khang yangs shing rgya
NK010(tha)004:497: che ba'i nang du gtor rdzas zhing bcu'i dgra bgegs
NK010(tha)004:498: kyi gzugs phung nang khrol du lhu dum dang bcas
NK010(tha)004:499: pa h'u mthing gas mtshan par gyur /
NK010(tha)004:502: sam ha ra na h'u gis 'khor 'das kyi dwangs
NK010(tha)004:503: bcud bdud rtsi la bsdus par bsams la gtor gzhong
NK010(tha)004:505: ma h+aa ba ling+ta te dz+wa ba ling+ta ba la b+aa d+ya gu h+ya sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK010(tha)004:507: gzugs rdo rje ma la sogs 'dod yon gyi lha
NK010(tha)004:508: mo ma tshang ba med pa'i rang bzhin du 'char
NK010(tha)004:509: bar gyur / mo thod du gnas pa'i rak+ta bsang sbyangs /
NK010(tha)004:510: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum pad+ma b+hany+dza ka p+aa la b+h+r+aum /
NK010(tha)004:511: dmar gyi dung chen yum gyi pad+ma'i rang bzhin yangs
NK010(tha)004:512: shing rgya che ba'i nang du du ra las rak+ta'i
NK010(tha)004:513: rgya mtsho'i steng du pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma bzhi
NK010(tha)004:514: pa'i dbus su a yig dmar pos mtshan par gyur
NK010(tha)004:517: sam ha ra na h'u gis zhing bcu'i sha khrag
NK010(tha)004:518: drangs te rak+ta la thim par bsams la pad+ma 'khyil
NK010(tha)004:520: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h'u h+r+aihth+aah lan
NK010(tha)004:521: bdun brjod nas zhal gzar gyis dkrugs shing 'phyar bas
NK010(tha)004:522: / lbu ba'i rlabs la mi ro dang rta ro'i snas dang /
NK010(tha)004:523: khro bo rta mgrin gyi rdul phra rab 'phro bas phyogs bcu'i gdon bgegs rnams tshar bcad /
NK010(tha)004:524: khams gsum gyi 'dod chags bag la nyal stongs par gyur par bsam mo //
NK010(tha)004:525: bsnyen pa spros med la sogs pa'i tshe de tsam
NK010(tha)004:526: ma nus na dmigs pa rnams nyams 'og tu tshud
NK010(tha)004:527: pa byas la so so'i so sor rang sngags kyis
NK010(tha)004:529: spyi don gnyis pa dngos gzhi la bzhi /
NK010(tha)004:530: bskyed gzhi'i ting nge 'dzin gsum byang chub kyi sems
NK010(tha)004:531: rnam pa gnyis su bsdu ba'i khyad par bshad pa
NK010(tha)004:532: / bskyed rim gyi ngo bos dag pa'i snod bcud bsgrub pa /
NK010(tha)004:533: rang bzhin ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dang gnyis med du bya ba /
NK010(tha)004:534: de la tshogs gnyis 'bras bu dang bcas pa bsgrub pa'o //
NK010(tha)004:535: dang po bskyed gzhi'i bsam gtan gsum ni rdo rje khros pa rtsa bshad gnyis dang /
NK010(tha)004:536: 'bar ba rtsa dum la sogs pa myang 'das lta
NK010(tha)004:537: bu'i dngos bstan las gzhan pa'i khyad chos bshad kyang
NK010(tha)004:538: snga rabs pa rnams kyis 'grel tshul ji bzhin rngo
NK010(tha)004:539: ma thogs par da dung ting 'dzin gsum la dngos
NK010(tha)004:540: tshig bsnan pas bzlos par gyur la /
NK010(tha)004:541: de'i phyir rgyud kyi rdo rje'i gnas chen po 'di yin te /
NK010(tha)004:542: sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs rnam par mi rtog cing
NK010(tha)004:543: 'gyur ba med pa rdo rje'i rang bzhin ni lam
NK010(tha)004:544: dus su de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin du
NK010(tha)004:545: ngang gis gnas pa'i rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge
NK010(tha)004:547: de nyid rtogs nas dang po na yod pa'i lhag
NK010(tha)004:548: bsam rnam dag gi sems rang shugs la skye bas
NK010(tha)004:549: snying rje'i mi mthun phyogs zhe sdang gi kun tu
NK010(tha)004:550: rtog pa la rang bzhin khros pa lta bu'i zhe
NK010(tha)004:551: sdang me long lta bu'i ye shes su gcod pa
NK010(tha)004:552: ni zhe sdang rdo rje'i mtshan nyid yin no //
NK010(tha)004:553: tshul de bzhin du rin po che'i rigs mnyam pa
NK010(tha)004:554: nyid kyi lta ba ni nyon mongs pa nga rgyal
NK010(tha)004:555: la khros pa lta bu'i nga rgyal mnyam pa nyid
NK010(tha)004:556: kyi ye shes su gcod pa ni nga rgyal rdo
NK010(tha)004:558: 'dod chags la sogs pa gzhan gsum la'ang sbyang gzhi
NK010(tha)004:559: sbyong byed de ltar gnas pa ni kun snang dpal
NK010(tha)004:561: de ltar stong nyid snying rje chen po zung du
NK010(tha)004:562: 'brel ba'i mtshon bya don gyi nam mkha' skye ba
NK010(tha)004:563: med pa'i dbyings las 'gag med thugs rje chen pos
NK010(tha)004:564: rol pa bcud du 'dril ba'i thig pa ye ge
NK010(tha)004:565: h'u sngon la sogs ye shes lnga'i rang 'od can
NK010(tha)004:566: du 'phro zhing 'bar ba'i rnam pa 'khor 'das mtha'
NK010(tha)004:567: dag pa'i srog gi go ru shar ba ni rgyu'i
NK010(tha)004:568: ting nge 'dzin sgyu ma lta bu'i rang bzhin can
NK010(tha)004:569: no // de ltar 'khor 'das thams cad kyi srog
NK010(tha)004:570: gi gor 'char ba'i rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin ye shes
NK010(tha)004:571: lnga'i rang 'od can du 'bar ba gang zhig snying
NK010(tha)004:572: ga la sogs pa gzugs kyi phung por 'dzin pa'i
NK010(tha)004:573: gnas lnga'i gor shar bas rnam par shes pa la
NK010(tha)004:574: sogs pa'i phung po lnga sangs rgyas lnga'i rang bzhin
NK010(tha)004:575: du 'grub pa'i rgyu byed cing de'i mi mthun phyogs
NK010(tha)004:576: nyon mongs pa lnga tshar gcod pa'i rten 'brel sgrig
NK010(tha)004:577: pa ni phur pa ye shes rtse mo'i rgyud kyi
NK010(tha)004:579: de dag gi don rgyud gzhung gis ston pa ni /
NK010(tha)004:582: rdo rje khros pas zhe sdang gcod //
NK010(tha)004:583: thugs ni yang dag rdo rje nyid //
NK010(tha)004:584: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes te //
NK010(tha)004:585: rnam par mi rtog rtog las 'das //
NK010(tha)004:586: de bzhin nyid du bsgom par bya //
NK010(tha)004:587: de ni chos kyi sku nyid las //
NK010(tha)004:588: bzhin ni ma nor ba yang yin //
NK010(tha)004:589: nyid ni bcos su med pa'o //
NK010(tha)004:590: mtshon chen sngon po 'bar ba yi //
NK010(tha)004:591: nam mkha'i dkyil nas thig pa shar //
NK010(tha)004:592: srog gi go ru shar ba dang //
NK010(tha)004:593: snying gi go ru bsgom par bya //
NK010(tha)004:595: rin chen khros pas nga rgyal gcod //
NK010(tha)004:597: nam mkha'i dkyil nas thig pa shar //
NK010(tha)004:598: lte ba'i go ru bsgom par bya //
NK010(tha)004:600: 'khor lo khroos pas gti mug gcod //
NK010(tha)004:602: nam mkha'i dkyil nas thig pa shar //
NK010(tha)004:603: klad pa'i go ru bsgom par bya //
NK010(tha)004:607: nam mkha'i dkyil nas thig pa shar //
NK010(tha)004:608: mgrin pa'i go ru bsgom par bya //
NK010(tha)004:610: sna tshogs khros pas phrag dog gcod //
NK010(tha)004:612: nam mkha'i dkyil nas thig pa shar //
NK010(tha)004:613: rkang pa'i go ru bsgom par bya //
NK010(tha)004:614: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug dang //
NK010(tha)004:615: nga rgyal phrag dog rnam pa lnga'i //
NK010(tha)004:616: rdo rje'i dam tshig chen po ni //
NK010(tha)004:617: rnam grol chen po'i ting 'dzin te //
NK010(tha)004:618: rang bzhin med par gsad par bya //
NK010(tha)004:619: zhes pas rgyu ma rig pa dang /
NK010(tha)004:620: rkyen nyon mongs pa lnga'i dug gis bskyed pa'i chos
NK010(tha)004:621: can thams cad rang gi mtshan nyid kyis ma grub
NK010(tha)004:622: pa'i gshis stong pa nyid kyi ngang du gsad pa
NK010(tha)004:623: ni don dam pa'i byang chub kyi sems so //
NK010(tha)004:624: de'i ngang nas lhag pa'i bsam pas kun rdzob byang
NK010(tha)004:625: chub kyi sems rdo rje'i rnal 'byor du bskyed pa
NK010(tha)004:626: ni / sems can rnams 'khor ba'i rgya ma tsho
NK010(tha)004:627: las bsgral 'dod kyi blo tshad med bzhi'i dam tshig
NK010(tha)004:628: ni / ste / gnod sems kyi blo dang lhan cig mi gnas par nges pas /
NK010(tha)004:630: byams dang snying rje dga' ba dang //
NK010(tha)004:631: btang snyoms bzhis bsgral dam tshig ni //
NK010(tha)004:632: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK010(tha)004:633: phung po rdo rjes gtams byas nas //
NK010(tha)004:634: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK010(tha)004:635: de la phung po rdo rje'i sgra don mi chod
NK010(tha)004:636: pa mi shigs pa sogs chos bdun dang ldan pa
NK010(tha)004:637: yin pa'i stong pa snying rje'i ros gang ba'i ye
NK010(tha)004:638: shes rdo rjes bdag dang sems can thams cad kyi
NK010(tha)004:639: ming bzhi'i phung po gtams nas /
NK010(tha)004:640: rnam par shes pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK010(tha)004:641: kyi thugs rdo rje'i rang bzhin yi ge h'u mthing
NK010(tha)004:642: nag 'od zer kun tu 'phro bar bsgom pa ni
NK010(tha)004:643: skyed byed 'grub pa'i rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK010(tha)004:645: rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa dang /
NK010(tha)004:646: brten pa'i lha tshogs bskyed pa'o //
NK010(tha)004:647: dang po la gzhal yas khang dang /
NK010(tha)004:649: dang po ni rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin de nyid las
NK010(tha)004:650: gzhal med khang gi rten gzhi 'byung ba rim brtsegs
NK010(tha)004:652: phyi snod kyi 'byung chen lnga dang /
NK010(tha)004:653: nang bcud kyi 'byung chung lnga po yum lnga'i mkha'
NK010(tha)004:654: klong rnam par dag pa'i gor shar ba'i steng du
NK010(tha)004:655: ye shes kyi gzhal med khang bskyed pa'i tshul /
NK010(tha)004:657: h'u e yam ram sum kem ram b+h+r+aum /
NK010(tha)004:658: b+h+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK010(tha)004:659: srog las nam mkha' gru gsum dang //
NK010(tha)004:660: rlung khrag sha chen keng rus me //
NK010(tha)004:661: 'jigs pa'i dur khrod gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)004:662: sgra yi rkyen gyis rab tu rdzogs //
NK010(tha)004:664: mdzes shing 'jigs par rab tu gnas //
NK010(tha)004:665: phyi ni rin chen lnga las grub //
NK010(tha)004:666: dbus su nor bu bee d+aur+ya //
NK010(tha)004:667: shar ni shel yin lho ni gser //
NK010(tha)004:668: nub ni pad+ma r+aa ga la //
NK010(tha)004:669: byang gi in+d+ra n+ai lar gnas //
NK010(tha)004:670: rin chen lnga yi rtsigs pas mdzes //
NK010(tha)004:671: 'dod yon lha mo rin chen brdar //
NK010(tha)004:672: me tog phreng ba mu tig har //
NK010(tha)004:673: t+wa ra na zhing 'khor lo gdugs //
NK010(tha)004:674: ba dan la sogs rab tu mdzes //
NK010(tha)004:675: tog ni rdo rje rtse dgu pa'o //
NK010(tha)004:676: nang ni dur khrod gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)004:677: klu chen brgyad kyi ka ba la //
NK010(tha)004:678: nyi ma zla ba lha yi bu //
NK010(tha)004:679: ka gdan ka gzhu mdzes par gnas //
NK010(tha)004:680: lha chen brgyad kyi gdung la ni //
NK010(tha)004:681: zla ba'i skar khung yang dag gnas //
NK010(tha)004:682: gza' chen brgyad kyi lcam la ni //
NK010(tha)004:683: nyi ma'i mthong khung bcu yis mdzes //
NK010(tha)004:684: nyi shu rtsa brgyad rgyu skar gyis //
NK010(tha)004:685: gral ma rnams su rab tu mdzes //
NK010(tha)004:686: thod pa skam rlon ra ris kyis //
NK010(tha)004:687: phyogs bzhi'i rtsig pa rab tu byas //
NK010(tha)004:688: 'byung po bsnol bas ma theb byas //
NK010(tha)004:689: chu srin ya theb nyid du byas //
NK010(tha)004:690: ro rlon logs kyi skyes bu la //
NK010(tha)004:691: rigs bzhi klu yi sgo bzhi mdzes //
NK010(tha)004:692: dbus kyi gru gsum mthing nag la //
NK010(tha)004:693: zla gam dmar po gsum dang ldan //
NK010(tha)004:694: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad nag por gnas //
NK010(tha)004:695: dur khrod brgyad du gnas pa ste //
NK010(tha)004:696: mtsho dang rlung dang sprin dang ni //
NK010(tha)004:697: zhing skyong phyogs skyong mchod rten dang //
NK010(tha)004:698: brag dang me yi rnam par gnas //
NK010(tha)004:699: ro ni rlon pa ra ri dang //
NK010(tha)004:700: keng rus bam rul rnam par 'thor //
NK010(tha)004:701: bya gcan 'jigs pa'i ma mo dang //
NK010(tha)004:702: srid pa'i mkha' 'gro mang po gnas //
NK010(tha)004:703: gzhal yas mdzes shing 'jigs pa der //
NK010(tha)004:704: gnyis pa gdan bskyed pa ni /
NK010(tha)004:705: r+au tra kro d+hi ti ra bam /
NK010(tha)004:709: r+au tra pho mo dam sri bcu //
NK010(tha)004:710: bdud bzhi bgegs bzhi pho mo rnams //
NK010(tha)004:711: kha sbub gan rkyal byi chings mnan //
NK010(tha)004:712: pad+ma nyi zla yon tan spras //
NK010(tha)004:714: gnyis pa brten pa'i lha bskyed pa la gnyis /
NK010(tha)004:715: gzhan gyi sras su bdag bya ba dang /
NK010(tha)004:716: bdag gi sras su gzhan bya ba'i tshul lo //
NK010(tha)004:717: dang po ye shes rtse mor las /
NK010(tha)004:718: ji ltar sangs rgyas thugs las byung //
NK010(tha)004:719: lhun gyis grub pa'i cho ga dang //
NK010(tha)004:720: cho ga'i yan lag rdzogs pa la //
NK010(tha)004:721: mkhas pa sangs rgyas sras yin no //
NK010(tha)004:722: zhes pas rdo rje cho ga gsum gyis rgyu'i he
NK010(tha)004:723: ru ka zhi ba las bardzusa skyes khro bor skad
NK010(tha)004:724: cig gis gnas 'gyur ba'i tshul las bskyed pa ste
NK010(tha)004:726: rdo rje h'u yig yongs gyur las //
NK010(tha)004:727: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum ni //
NK010(tha)004:728: mtshan dang dpe byad yang dag rdzogs //
NK010(tha)004:729: rdo rje dril bu bde bar 'khyud //
NK010(tha)004:730: kun+da lta bur dkar ba'i mdog /
NK010(tha)004:731: rigs lnga khrag 'thung yab yum bcu //
NK010(tha)004:732: 'dus pa'i rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku //
NK010(tha)004:733: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya d+aip+ta tsakra ha
NK010(tha)004:734: na ha na ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u
NK010(tha)004:735: / zhe sdang khrag 'thung rgyal po dang //
NK010(tha)004:736: bde bar sgrol bar byed pa'i yum //
NK010(tha)004:737: khro zhing rngams pa'i tshul bskyed pas //
NK010(tha)004:738: gdug pa ma lus sgrol bar byed //
NK010(tha)004:739: a dang h'u las rab tu sbyar //
NK010(tha)004:740: yum gyis yab kyi lce gzhibs nas //
NK010(tha)004:741: yum gyi thugs kar ut+pala gtad //
NK010(tha)004:742: gdung ba'i nga ros 'di skad brjod //
NK010(tha)004:744: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK010(tha)004:745: srid pa rdo rjer grub mdzod cig /
NK010(tha)004:746: srid pa rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NK010(tha)004:747: ye shes khro bor grub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:751: srid pa 'khor lor grub mdzod cig /
NK010(tha)004:752: srid pa 'khor lo phur pa'i lha //
NK010(tha)004:753: ye shes khro bor grub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:755: rin chen gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK010(tha)004:756: srid pa rin chen grub mdzod cig /
NK010(tha)004:757: srid pa rin chen phur pa'i lha //
NK010(tha)004:758: ye shes khro bor grub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:761: srid pa pad+mara grub mdzod cig /
NK010(tha)004:762: srid pa pad+ma phur pa'i lha //
NK010(tha)004:763: ye shes khro bor grub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:765: sna tshogs gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK010(tha)004:766: srid pa ral grir grub mdzod cig /
NK010(tha)004:767: srid pa ral gri phur pa'i lha //
NK010(tha)004:768: ye shes khro bor grub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:771: sras dang btsun mo bcas pa ni //
NK010(tha)004:772: 'khor ba'i chos las skyes pa ste //
NK010(tha)004:773: sems can gyi ni sras su bya //
NK010(tha)004:775: yab yum sbyor ba mdzad pa las //
NK010(tha)004:776: dgyes mchod gsang ba so sor thob //
NK010(tha)004:777: s+pha ra na phata brjod pas //
NK010(tha)004:778: 'od kyis sras bcas rgyal ba mchod //
NK010(tha)004:779: sems can kun gyi sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK010(tha)004:780: sam ha ra na h'u brjod pas //
NK010(tha)004:781: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams //
NK010(tha)004:782: bkug nas yum gyi mkha' ru bstim //
NK010(tha)004:783: bde chen byang chub sems su gyur //
NK010(tha)004:784: rdo rje'i dam tshig e ma ho //
NK010(tha)004:785: gnyis med dgyes pa chen po'i ngang //
NK010(tha)004:786: yab yum 'od zhu yi ge h'u //
NK010(tha)004:787: yongs gyur 'bras bu'i he ru ka /
NK010(tha)004:788: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK010(tha)004:789: sgeg pa dpa' ba gar dgu pa //
NK010(tha)004:790: rdzu 'phrul zhabs bzhi dor stabs bsgrad //
NK010(tha)004:791: rnam par thar pa'i dbu gsum gyi //
NK010(tha)004:792: skrag mdzad bzhad gshe khro bo'i zhal //
NK010(tha)004:793: g.yas pa ljang nag g.yon dmar nag /
NK010(tha)004:794: spyan dmar smin ma sma ra ser //
NK010(tha)004:795: khro gnyer chu yi rlabs bzhin 'khrugs //
NK010(tha)004:796: pha rol phyin drug mtshon pa yi //
NK010(tha)004:797: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po na //
NK010(tha)004:798: gser gyi rdo rje rtse dgu dang //
NK010(tha)004:799: g.yon gyi dang po me dpung bsnams //
NK010(tha)004:800: g.yas pa rdo rje rtse lnga dang //
NK010(tha)004:801: dgra s+t+wa rdo rje tho ba'o //
NK010(tha)004:802: slob dpon chen pos chos rgyal gi thugs dam du
NK010(tha)004:803: bzhag pa rdo rje bkod pa rnal 'byor chen po'i
NK010(tha)004:804: rgyud kyi le'u dgu pa sgra ji bzhin pa'o //
NK010(tha)004:805: kha t+w+aam thod dbyug lcags kyu g.yon //
NK010(tha)004:806: g.yas kyi tha ma phur pa dang //
NK010(tha)004:807: g.yon na phra men rbod gtong ni //
NK010(tha)004:808: khyung dang bya rgod 'ug pa dang //
NK010(tha)004:809: khra dang bya rog pho nyar 'gyed //
NK010(tha)004:810: rdo rje'i gshog pas srid gsum gnon //
NK010(tha)004:811: mthing nag sku la dur khrod brgyan //
NK010(tha)004:812: rigs lnga thod pa lnga yis brgyan //
NK010(tha)004:813: klu chen brgyad dang thod pas brgyan //
NK010(tha)004:816: sbrul dang thod pa gzig gis brgyan //
NK010(tha)004:817: dril bu thod khrag phyag na bsnams //
NK010(tha)004:818: e ka dza ti sgrol ba'i yum //
NK010(tha)004:820: gri gug thod khrag khams gsum sgrol /
NK010(tha)004:821: re 'ga' kha t+w+aam rtse gsum bsnams //
NK010(tha)004:822: g.yer kha dril bu nyid las yang //
NK010(tha)004:823: rtog med chos kyi sgra 'byin ma //
NK010(tha)004:824: ma mo drug cu pho nyar 'gyed //
NK010(tha)004:825: de nas snyoms par zhugs nas thog mar mkha' gsang
NK010(tha)004:826: brlabs shing sras 'byin gyi sbyor ba bsgrub pa ni
NK010(tha)004:827: / h'u las yab kyi gsang gnas ni //
NK010(tha)004:828: rdo rje rtse lngar zla dkyil +amo //
NK010(tha)004:829: pam las yum mkha' pad 'dab brgyad //
NK010(tha)004:830: ze 'bru nyi mar mum gyis mtshan //
NK010(tha)004:831: sa ma ya ho yab kyi brda' //
NK010(tha)004:832: sa ma ya s+t+wam yum gyi lan //
NK010(tha)004:833: r+aa ga ya ho yab kyi brda' //
NK010(tha)004:834: r+aa ga ya mi yum gyi lan //
NK010(tha)004:835: dzah h'u bam hohphyaga rgya bzhis //
NK010(tha)004:836: thal gong sked skabs dbang po'i sgo //
NK010(tha)004:837: bo la ka ko la rnams sprad //
NK010(tha)004:838: chags pa lcags kyu zhes bya ste //
NK010(tha)004:840: pad+mara chud pa zhags pa mo //
NK010(tha)004:841: kha phyed ma ni sgrog yin te //
NK010(tha)004:842: sgra grags ma ni dril bu'o //
NK010(tha)004:843: pad+ma yo gi ni pra we sha ya phata /
NK010(tha)004:844: 'dod chags chen po'i tshul gyis ni //
NK010(tha)004:845: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun bsdus te //
NK010(tha)004:846: 'khor rnams thugs la zhugs pa yis //
NK010(tha)004:847: shes rab ma ni dga' bar bya //
NK010(tha)004:848: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK010(tha)004:849: gsang ba 'di las gzhan med de //
NK010(tha)004:850: kun rdzob dang ni don dam gyi //
NK010(tha)004:851: chos kun byang chub sems su gnas //
NK010(tha)004:852: dang por babs pas gzhal med khang //
NK010(tha)004:854: gnyis pa gdan gyur gsum pa las //
NK010(tha)004:855: yab kyi rtog tshogs yi ger rdzogs //
NK010(tha)004:856: b+ha ga nyid du lha rnams bsam //
NK010(tha)004:857: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya phata dzah +aahmh'u k+aa
NK010(tha)004:858: ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra dz+ny+aa na +aa be sha
NK010(tha)004:861: kro ta kro ti ha he phata /
NK010(tha)004:863: ma h+aa sa na sa ma ya hoh h'u h'u badz+ra g+han+da badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK010(tha)004:864: sarba big nan bam h'u h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:865: d+aip+ta tsakra ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:866: ma h+aa bo d+hi tsit+ta man+da la h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:867: yab yum 'dod chags nga ro brjod //
NK010(tha)004:868: byin gnyis dam du rab 'khyud de //
NK010(tha)004:869: lag pa dam 'khyud ma mchu gzhibs //
NK010(tha)004:870: rdo rje'i dam tshig glu yis bskul //
NK010(tha)004:872: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK010(tha)004:873: ngang nyid rdo rje'i chos dbyings las //
NK010(tha)004:874: 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)004:875: sku yi dbyig tu sras bskyed cig /
NK010(tha)004:877: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK010(tha)004:878: ngang nyid 'khor lo'i chos dbyings las //
NK010(tha)004:879: 'khor lo'i khro bo mi bzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)004:880: sku yi dbyig tu sras bskyed cig /
NK010(tha)004:882: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK010(tha)004:883: ngang nyid rin chen chos dbyings las //
NK010(tha)004:884: rin chen khro bo mi bzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)004:885: sku yi dbyig tu sras bskyed cig /
NK010(tha)004:887: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK010(tha)004:888: ngang nyid pad+ma'i chos dbyings las //
NK010(tha)004:889: pad+ma'i khro bo mi bzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)004:890: sku yi dbyig tu sras bskyed cig /
NK010(tha)004:892: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK010(tha)004:893: ngang nyid ral gri'i chos dbyings las //
NK010(tha)004:894: ral gri'i khro bo mi bzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)004:895: sku yi dbyig tu sras bskyed cig /
NK010(tha)004:896: ces bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor la bskul nas /
NK010(tha)004:897: phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor sras kyi rang bzhin du bskyed pa ni /
NK010(tha)004:898: de brjod bde ba'i rba rlabs kyis //
NK010(tha)004:899: yi ge 'joms byed sgra yis bskyed //
NK010(tha)004:900: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big nan bam h+aum h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)004:901: +amo bud+d+ha k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big nan bam h+aum h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)004:902: +amo rat+na k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big nan bam h+aum h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)004:903: +amo pad+ma k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big nan bam h'u h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:904: +amo karma k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big nan bam h'u h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:905: sras mchog rdo rje phur pa ni //
NK010(tha)004:906: yum gyi b+ha gar sku gsum rdzogs //
NK010(tha)004:907: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah de brjod yab kyi phyag gis blangs //
NK010(tha)004:908: phyag ni rigs lnga yab yum bcu //
NK010(tha)004:909: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK010(tha)004:910: bde ba'i rlabs kyis dbang bzhi bskur //
NK010(tha)004:911: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya +aa we sha ya h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:912: rigs lnga'i dbu yi gtsug tor can //
NK010(tha)004:913: rdo rje rin chen pad+ma las //
NK010(tha)004:914: de bzhin rigs kyi sras mchog lnga //
NK010(tha)004:915: stod ni gtso bo yab 'dra la //
NK010(tha)004:916: smad ni chu srin phur pa'i dbal //
NK010(tha)004:918: sku gcig ngang la sku gsum rdzogs //
NK010(tha)004:919: rgya mdud nang nas sngags kyi sgra //
NK010(tha)004:920: 'brug stong lta bur ldir zhing sgrogs //
NK010(tha)004:921: chu srin kha nang me lce 'od //
NK010(tha)004:922: glog ltar 'khyud cing stong gsum gsal //
NK010(tha)004:924: stong gsum gang zhing klu rnams 'dul //
NK010(tha)004:925: thugs ka dpal be'i dkyil 'khor na //
NK010(tha)004:926: bzhi bcu rtsa bdun lha tshogs dang //
NK010(tha)004:927: dbu la rigs lnga khrag 'thung rdzogs //
NK010(tha)004:928: dkyil 'khor yongs rdzogs bdag nyid can //
NK010(tha)004:929: dgra s+t+wa g.yas la rang rtags g.yon //
NK010(tha)004:930: bar pa kha t+w+aam gtun shing dang //
NK010(tha)004:931: tha ma ri rab phur bu 'dril //
NK010(tha)004:932: rgyud lnga ye shes lnga ru sgrol //
NK010(tha)004:933: dug lnga rtsad nas gcod par byed //
NK010(tha)004:934: sangs rgyas 'dus pa thams cad kyi //
NK010(tha)004:935: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs //
NK010(tha)004:936: +amo bud+d+ha k+ai li k+ai la ya k+aa ya badz+ra nan /
NK010(tha)004:937: dz+wa la dz+wa la pra dz+wa la pra dz+wa la /
NK010(tha)004:938: s+phu ta s+phu ta sarba na sa pa na ye h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:939: +amo pad+ma k+ai li k+ai la ya w+aa k+ka badz+ra nan /
NK010(tha)004:940: sarba dush+tam h+r+aih shod+ha ya h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:941: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya badz+ra tsit+ta nan /
NK010(tha)004:943: lus kyi ba spu'i bu ga kun //
NK010(tha)004:944: khro chung nyid kyis rab tu gtams //
NK010(tha)004:945: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK010(tha)004:946: be t+aa li man+da la rak+sha rak+sha h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:947: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:948: lus kyi bkrag dang ldan pa dang //
NK010(tha)004:949: ba spu'i bu ga rdo rjes gtams //
NK010(tha)004:950: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK010(tha)004:951: ma gu ta la pra ta la h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:954: khro bo du mas byin gyis brlabs //
NK010(tha)004:955: khams gsum gdug pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)004:956: gdul bya'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK010(tha)004:958: zhes phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor dang gnyis su med par bsam mo //
NK010(tha)004:959: de nas phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK010(tha)004:960: mtshan sngags kyis khro bcu so so dang /
NK010(tha)004:962: gardza la sogs pa gnyis gnyis las khra thabs rnams byung /
NK010(tha)004:964: gtso bo yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams las thon te phyogs skyong gi gdan la 'khod par bsams la /
NK010(tha)004:965: de nas phyogs skyong tshar gcad phyir /
NK010(tha)004:967: h'u sgra drag pos snyoms par zhugs //
NK010(tha)004:968: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK010(tha)004:969: khro bor gyur pas phyogs skyong bcu //
NK010(tha)004:970: sde dang bcas pa tshar bcad de //
NK010(tha)004:971: srog snying phrogs nas stan du bting //
NK010(tha)004:981: pri thi b+ai b+h+ya ti ra bam dzahmh'u bam hoh de nas 'dod chags chen po yis //
NK010(tha)004:982: gsang ba'i pad+ma rgyas mdzad nas //
NK010(tha)004:983: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer dag /
NK010(tha)004:984: gsang ba'i dbyings su bstim par bya //
NK010(tha)004:985: byang chub sems kyi sgo nga las //
NK010(tha)004:986: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor thams cad ni //
NK010(tha)004:987: thugs ka nas ni phyung gyur te //
NK010(tha)004:988: khros pa'i dkyil 'khor nyid du bzhugs //
NK010(tha)004:989: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha h'u k+aa ra h'u /
NK010(tha)004:992: steng phyogs nyi zla'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)004:993: khro bo rdo rje h'u mdzad ni //
NK010(tha)004:994: zhal g.yas sngo zhing g.yon pa dmar //
NK010(tha)004:995: dbus zhal sku ni dkar ba'o //
NK010(tha)004:996: rdo rje dung khrag rig ma 'khyud //
NK010(tha)004:997: rdo rje tho ba g.yas pa ste //
NK010(tha)004:998: mda' gzhu spu gri g.yon pa'o //
NK010(tha)004:999: yum chen rdo rje sgra 'byin ma //
NK010(tha)004:1000: sprul pa phag dang smig bu'i mgo //
NK010(tha)004:1001: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h'u /
NK010(tha)004:1004: shar rtsibs dri za'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)004:1005: khro bo rdo rje rnam par rgyal //
NK010(tha)004:1006: dbus dkar g.yas sngo ljang ser g.yon //
NK010(tha)004:1007: dang po rdo rje dung chen te //
NK010(tha)004:1009: ti ra bya rgod tha ma 'dzin //
NK010(tha)004:1010: brag gi steng na brgya byin gnon //
NK010(tha)004:1011: rdo rje'i rgyan rnams rdzogs par btags //
NK010(tha)004:1012: yum chen rdo rje snyems ma dang //
NK010(tha)004:1013: sprul pa stag dang bla rgod mgo //
NK010(tha)004:1014: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha ni la dan+da h'u /
NK010(tha)004:1017: shar lho me lha'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)004:1018: dbyug pa sngon po sngo skya dbus //
NK010(tha)004:1019: g.yas dkar g.yon ni dmar skya ste //
NK010(tha)004:1020: rdo rje dung chen dbyug pa me //
NK010(tha)004:1021: ti ra'i dbyug pa kha yis mdzes //
NK010(tha)004:1022: 'bar ba zhabs drug drang srong gnon //
NK010(tha)004:1023: yum chen rdo rje sder mo dang //
NK010(tha)004:1024: sprul pa g.yag dang bya rog mgo //
NK010(tha)004:1025: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha ya man+ta ka h'u /
NK010(tha)004:1028: lho phyogs gshin rje'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)004:1029: gshin rje'i rgyal po sngon po ste //
NK010(tha)004:1030: sngo skya ljang nag g.yon gyi dbu //
NK010(tha)004:1031: dung khrag thod dbug dgra s+t+wa bsnams //
NK010(tha)004:1032: ti ra bya rog tha mar mdzes //
NK010(tha)004:1034: yum chen dur khrod bdag mo dang //
NK010(tha)004:1035: sprul pa sha ba 'ug pa'i mgo //
NK010(tha)004:1036: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h'u /
NK010(tha)004:1039: lho nub srin po'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)004:1040: mi g.yo ljang sngon 'bar ba'i zhal //
NK010(tha)004:1041: sngon po smug nag g.yon gyi dbu //
NK010(tha)004:1042: dung khrag ral gri zhags pas brgyan //
NK010(tha)004:1043: ti ra 'ug pas rgyan par mdzes //
NK010(tha)004:1044: bden bral btsir bar mdzad pa ste //
NK010(tha)004:1045: rgyan rnams rdzogs par yang dag btags //
NK010(tha)004:1046: yum chen rdo rje gtun khung dang //
NK010(tha)004:1047: sprul pa gzig dang khwa ta'i mgo //
NK010(tha)004:1048: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha h+ya g+r+ai wa h+r+aih hu lu h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:1050: nub phyogs klu yi gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)004:1051: rta skad dmar po g.yas dkar po //
NK010(tha)004:1052: g.yon ni sngon po rnam par mdzes //
NK010(tha)004:1053: dung khrag zhags pa spu gri can //
NK010(tha)004:1054: ti ra mkha' lding tha mar mdzes //
NK010(tha)004:1055: dug gi steng na zhabs gnyis brkyang //
NK010(tha)004:1056: rdo rje rta yi rgyal po btags //
NK010(tha)004:1057: yum chen rdo rje gtum mo dang //
NK010(tha)004:1058: sprul pa byi la pu shud mgo //
NK010(tha)004:1059: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha a pa ra dzi ta h'u /
NK010(tha)004:1062: nub byang rlung lha'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)004:1063: gzhan las rgyal ba dmar skya ste //
NK010(tha)004:1064: ser po ljang gu g.yon gyi zhal //
NK010(tha)004:1065: dung khrag dpal mda' rnga yab can //
NK010(tha)004:1066: ti ra skye ka yang dag 'dzin //
NK010(tha)004:1067: rlung gi steng na zhabs brkyang ste //
NK010(tha)004:1068: 'bar ba'i rgyan rnams tshang bar btags //
NK010(tha)004:1069: yum chen rdo rje mda' snyems ma //
NK010(tha)004:1070: sprul pa spyang ki khra yi mgo //
NK010(tha)004:1071: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h'u /
NK010(tha)004:1074: byang phyogs gnod sbyin gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)004:1075: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang nag mdog /
NK010(tha)004:1076: ser po dud kha g.yon gyi zhal //
NK010(tha)004:1077: dung khrag dbyug to rgya gram ste //
NK010(tha)004:1078: ti ra'i dbyug pa pu shud can //
NK010(tha)004:1079: gsus pa 'phyangs pa rnam par bardzisa //
NK010(tha)004:1080: 'bar ba chen po rnam par btags //
NK010(tha)004:1081: yum chen rdo rje rlung 'byin dang //
NK010(tha)004:1082: sprul pa seng ge pha wang mgo //
NK010(tha)004:1083: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha tree lokya bi dza ye h'u /
NK010(tha)004:1086: byang shar dbang ldan gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)004:1087: khams gsum kun las rgyal ba ni //
NK010(tha)004:1088: gser gyi mdog 'dra g.yas dkar te //
NK010(tha)004:1089: g.yon gyi dbu ni ljang dagu'o //
NK010(tha)004:1090: dung khrag lcags kyu ral gri g.yas //
NK010(tha)004:1091: rin chen pad+ma g.yon na bsnams //
NK010(tha)004:1092: yum chen rdo rje gsod ma dang //
NK010(tha)004:1093: sprul pa do ma dang sre mong mgo //
NK010(tha)004:1094: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa pa la h'u /
NK010(tha)004:1097: 'og phyogs sa bdag gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)004:1098: rdo rje khro bo stobs po che //
NK010(tha)004:1099: dbus nag g.yas dkar g.yon pa dmar //
NK010(tha)004:1100: rtsa phyag rdo rje dung khrag ste //
NK010(tha)004:1101: g.yas gnyis rdo rje zhags pa dang //
NK010(tha)004:1102: g.yon ni gshol dang gtun shing 'dzin //
NK010(tha)004:1103: kun kyang rdo rje'i gshog pa gdengs //
NK010(tha)004:1104: yum chen rdo rje bskyod ma dang //
NK010(tha)004:1105: sprul pa dred dang byi ba'i mgo //
NK010(tha)004:1106: yum rnams g.yas pa dril bu dang //
NK010(tha)004:1107: g.yon pa dung chen stob cing 'khyud //
NK010(tha)004:1108: stag dang gzig gi sham thabs can //
NK010(tha)004:1109: mche ba can dang gshog pa can //
NK010(tha)004:1110: phra men mgo brnyan nyi shu ni //
NK010(tha)004:1111: rtsibs mchan rnams la gnyis gnyis gnas //
NK010(tha)004:1112: zhal gcig phyag gnyis mdog nag gzugs //
NK010(tha)004:1113: sprul dang thod pas rab tu brgyan //
NK010(tha)004:1114: phur pa lcags kyu phyag na bsnams //
NK010(tha)004:1115: skra bardzesa spyan dmar mche ba gtsigs //
NK010(tha)004:1117: rnam 'gyur ma nges cir yang ston //
NK010(tha)004:1118: des nas bka' bsdod bskyed pa ni /
NK010(tha)004:1119: khyams kyi shar lho nub byang bzhir //
NK010(tha)004:1120: phrin las bzhi yi bdag nyid can //
NK010(tha)004:1121: b+h+yo yig bdun bdun spros pa ni //
NK010(tha)004:1122: yongs gyur dbang mo nyi shu brgyad //
NK010(tha)004:1123: gnas 'gyur gnyis pa gdong can gzugs //
NK010(tha)004:1124: drag shul chen po'i stabs kyis bzhugs //
NK010(tha)004:1125: sgo ma bzhi bskyed pa ni /
NK010(tha)004:1126: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya bi da ya bi da ya h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:1127: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya na mahs man+ta hrim hrim h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:1128: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya pra su ru pra su ru h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:1129: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya m+aa ra ya m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:1130: drod gsher las skyes sgo ma bzhi //
NK010(tha)004:1131: shar phyogs dri za'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)004:1132: skye ka'i mgo can lcags kyu ma //
NK010(tha)004:1133: lho phyogs grul bum gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)004:1134: pu shud mgo can zhags pa ma //
NK010(tha)004:1135: nub phyogs chu bdag gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)004:1136: srin bya'i mgo can lcags sgrog ma //
NK010(tha)004:1137: byang phyogs gnod sbyin gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)004:1138: khra yi mgo can dril bu ma //
NK010(tha)004:1139: 'di bzhi zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa //
NK010(tha)004:1140: dkar ser dmar dang ljang ba'i mdog /
NK010(tha)004:1141: gzig dang thod sbrul rgyan du byas //
NK010(tha)004:1142: bskum zhing brkyang ba'i zhabs kyis mnan //
NK010(tha)004:1143: phyag g.yon phur pa 'debs par mdzad //
NK010(tha)004:1144: me dpung dkyil na khro tshul bzhugs //
NK010(tha)004:1145: rtsa ba'i lha ni lnga bcu gnyis //
NK010(tha)004:1146: drag po'i tshul gyis zhe sdang 'joms //
NK010(tha)004:1147: de bzhin nga rgyal phrag dog dang //
NK010(tha)004:1148: 'dod chags gti mug gnas rigs drug /
NK010(tha)004:1150: rnam par gsod byed khro bo'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)004:1151: ting nge 'dzin las sprul pas na //
NK010(tha)004:1152: bgrang gis mi lang gzhal du med //
NK010(tha)004:1154: srid pa'i rtog pa 'joms la brtson //
NK010(tha)004:1155: mu ran la ni phur srung ste //
NK010(tha)004:1156: e yam ma ya bzhi nyid las //
NK010(tha)004:1157: shwa na mu kha bzhi po gsal //
NK010(tha)004:1158: dza yig bzhi las sa bdag bzhi //
NK010(tha)004:1159: b+h+yo yig bzhi las bdag nyid bzhi //
NK010(tha)004:1160: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul glog las myur //
NK010(tha)004:1161: bstan pa bsrung zhing nyams pa bdun //
NK010(tha)004:1162: zhe la gnag pa'i stobs kyis sgrol //
NK010(tha)004:1164: dpal chen dkyil 'khor gcig tu rdzogs //
NK010(tha)004:1165: de ltar brten pa'i dkyil 'khor gtso dang 'khor gyi
NK010(tha)004:1166: rnam rol du bskyed pa la bsnyen pa zhes bya
NK010(tha)004:1168: gtso dang 'khor dang rang bzhin ni //
NK010(tha)004:1169: rang rang bsnyen pa'i gzugs 'dzin to //
NK010(tha)004:1171: bskyed gzhi rang gi phung po khams dang skye mched
NK010(tha)004:1172: skra dang ba spu'i rnams grangs yan chod gdan gsum
NK010(tha)004:1173: tshang ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin du gnas pa
NK010(tha)004:1174: / skabs 'dir rdo rje phur pa'i sku'i rnam pa
NK010(tha)004:1175: go mtshams med par gyur pas gtams par bsam pa
NK010(tha)004:1176: ni nye bar bsnyen pa ste /
NK010(tha)004:1177: lus kyi rtags pa la sogs pa //
NK010(tha)004:1178: dam pa'i khro bo byin rlabs pa //
NK010(tha)004:1179: nyes bar gyur pa zhes bya ste //
NK010(tha)004:1180: zhes skyed byed grub pa'i rgyu ma nor ba bdag
NK010(tha)004:1181: nyid lhar gsal ba'i sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum
NK010(tha)004:1182: gyi ngo bor byin gyis brlabs pas khyad gzhi nges
NK010(tha)004:1183: par byas nas / de de ltar du byin gyis
NK010(tha)004:1184: slob pa dngos ni rang sngags dang bstun nas rdo
NK010(tha)004:1185: rje rtse lnga pa'i phyag rgya gnas so sor gtugs
NK010(tha)004:1186: par byas nas / shing / rdo rje 'bar ba las /
NK010(tha)004:1188: snying ga mgrin pa spyi bo ru //
NK010(tha)004:1189: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor bsam nas ni //
NK010(tha)004:1192: thugs kyi rdo rje la sogs bsgom //
NK010(tha)004:1193: de nyid shes rab sku rgyas ma //
NK010(tha)004:1194: lha mo rnams kyi 'od tshogs kyis //
NK010(tha)004:1195: dus gsum phyogs rnams khyab pa yis //
NK010(tha)004:1196: ma lus sangs rgyas drangs mchod nas //
NK010(tha)004:1197: bkra shis don byed rnams la ni //
NK010(tha)004:1198: rang gi thugs srog rdo rje yis //
NK010(tha)004:1199: de las byin brlabs bskul bar bya //
NK010(tha)004:1200: rdo rje thugs 'dzin dpal dang ldan //
NK010(tha)004:1201: rdo rje mi phyed gsum byed pa //
NK010(tha)004:1202: byin gyis brlabs kyi gnas byas te //
NK010(tha)004:1203: rdo rje thugs kar ldan par bya //
NK010(tha)004:1204: rdo rje mi byed gsum bsgom pas //
NK010(tha)004:1205: phyogs bcur bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK010(tha)004:1206: de la thugs las byung ba yis //
NK010(tha)004:1207: byin gyis brlabs kyi gnas mdzad do //
NK010(tha)004:1208: rdo rje'i phyag rgya snying gar bzhag la /
NK010(tha)004:1209: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK010(tha)004:1210: rdo rje gsung 'dzin dpal dang ldan //
NK010(tha)004:1211: rdo rje mi phyed gsum byed pa //
NK010(tha)004:1212: byin gyis brlabs kyi gnas byas te //
NK010(tha)004:1213: rdo rje gsung dang ldan par bya //
NK010(tha)004:1214: rdo rje mi phyed gsum bsgom pas //
NK010(tha)004:1215: phyogs bcur bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK010(tha)004:1216: de la gsung las byung ba yis //
NK010(tha)004:1217: byin gyis brlabs kyi gnas mdzad do //
NK010(tha)004:1218: phyag rgya mgrin par bzhag la /
NK010(tha)004:1219: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK010(tha)004:1220: rdo rje sku 'dzin dpal dang ldan //
NK010(tha)004:1221: rdo rje mi phyed gsum byed pa //
NK010(tha)004:1222: byin gyis brlabs kyi gnas byas te //
NK010(tha)004:1223: rdo rje sku dang ldan par byas //
NK010(tha)004:1224: rdo rje mi phyed gsum bsgom pas //
NK010(tha)004:1225: phyogs bcur bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK010(tha)004:1226: de la sku las byung ba yis //
NK010(tha)004:1227: byin gyis brlabs kyi gnas mdzad do //
NK010(tha)004:1228: phyag rgya spyi bor bzhag la /
NK010(tha)004:1229: +amo sarba th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK010(tha)004:1230: bsgrub pa chen po ni dbang bskur ba nyid la brjod de /
NK010(tha)004:1231: bsgrub pa chen po'i mtha' ru ni //
NK010(tha)004:1232: sangs rgyas rnams kyis dbang bskur te //
NK010(tha)004:1233: zhes pas 'dir phur pa'i sgos chos dang bcas pa'i dbang don nges par bya ba ni /
NK010(tha)004:1234: snying gar b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i gzhal med khang
NK010(tha)004:1235: sgo gcig pa'i sgo srung rta mgrin yab yum du
NK010(tha)004:1236: gnas pa'i nang du h'u las ye shes sems dpa'
NK010(tha)004:1237: tshon gang ba gcig bsam la /
NK010(tha)004:1238: ye shes dpa' bo'i thugs ka yi //
NK010(tha)004:1239: 'od kyis mgon po rnams bskul nas //
NK010(tha)004:1240: de dag thugs las byung ba yi //
NK010(tha)004:1241: rig mas bdud rtsi bum chu yis //
NK010(tha)004:1242: dbang bskur byas te thim gyur nas //
NK010(tha)004:1243: rang sngags rdo rje can gyis gzungs //
NK010(tha)004:1244: dbu rgyan rnams la rigs lnga dang //
NK010(tha)004:1245: rigs kyi bdag po rnams kyis brgyan //
NK010(tha)004:1246: ye shes sems dpa'i thugs ka'i 'od kyis phyogs bcu'i
NK010(tha)004:1247: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul
NK010(tha)004:1248: bas / de rnams kyi thugs ka nas byung ba'i
NK010(tha)004:1249: rdo rje btsun mo'i b+ha ga la gdan gsum tshang
NK010(tha)004:1250: ba'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs pa mdun gyi nam mkha' la
NK010(tha)004:1251: bas / byon / +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta
NK010(tha)004:1252: ma h+aa a nu r+aa ga dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa
NK010(tha)004:1254: zhes bskul bas lha tshogs rnams bde stong gi ros
NK010(tha)004:1255: tshims rjes chags kyi mes 'od du zhu ba'i bdud
NK010(tha)004:1256: rtsi bum pa'i chus mgo bo'i gnas lngar dbang bskur
NK010(tha)004:1257: / nyon mongs pa lnga'i dri ma sbyangs /
NK010(tha)004:1258: phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su gnas gyur
NK010(tha)004:1259: pa nas bzung ste khams dang skye mched thams cad
NK010(tha)004:1260: lha yi rang bzhin du rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)004:1261: dbang bzhi'i dam tshig las byung ba'i dga' ba bzhi'i ye shes nyams su myong /
NK010(tha)004:1262: chu lhag ma spyi bor brtan pa yongs su gyur
NK010(tha)004:1263: pa las rdo rje mi bskyod pa dbus su bzhugs
NK010(tha)004:1264: pa'i rigs lngas dbu brgyan par gyur par bsam pa
NK010(tha)004:1265: ni dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams kyis dkyil 'khor
NK010(tha)004:1266: gsum gyi srog ye shes su dbang bskur ba ste
NK010(tha)004:1268: thabs kyi spyod pa'i 'gro don du //
NK010(tha)004:1269: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK010(tha)004:1270: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)004:1271: dbang dang byin rlabs bdag stsol cig /
NK010(tha)004:1272: rdo rje phyi bsdam las gung mo brkyang ba mi bskyod pa'i dbang rgya spyi bor bzhag la /
NK010(tha)004:1273: +amo ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK010(tha)004:1274: de nas mdzub mo gnyis brkyang ba rnam snang gi dbang rgya dpral bar bzhag la /
NK010(tha)004:1275: +amo ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK010(tha)004:1276: srin lag brkyang ba rin 'byung gi dbang rgya rna ltag g.yas su bzhag la /
NK010(tha)004:1277: +amo ma h+aa sa ma t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK010(tha)004:1278: mthe bong brkyang ba snang mtha'i dbang rgya ltag par bzhag la /
NK010(tha)004:1279: +amo ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK010(tha)004:1280: mathe'u chung brkyang ba don grub kyi dbang rgya rna ltag g.yon du bzhag la /
NK010(tha)004:1281: +amo ma h+aa kri ta a nush+tha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swab+h+aa wa +aat+ma konya ham /
NK010(tha)004:1282: slar yang dkyil 'khor gsum las 'od dang yi ge
NK010(tha)004:1283: spros te sems can thams cad kyi nyon mongs pa'i
NK010(tha)004:1284: dug gzhil nas rigs drug gi sa bon du gyur
NK010(tha)004:1285: pas sbyang du rung bar byas /
NK010(tha)004:1286: 'byung ba gsum gyis bsreg gtor bkrus nas rdo rje
NK010(tha)004:1287: sems dpa'i rang bzhin du gyur pa snying ga'i rta
NK010(tha)004:1288: mgrin la 'dus par bsgom pa ni dkyil 'khor gsum
NK010(tha)004:1289: gyis khams gsum gyi srog la dbang bskur ba zhes
NK010(tha)004:1290: bya'o // rta mgrin yab yum kyang sbyor ba mdzad
