NK010(tha)004:1621: ye shes lnga po grub pa'i rtsi //
NK010(tha)004:1622: 'chi ba med pa'i dam rdzas che //
NK010(tha)004:1624: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa ti /
NK010(tha)004:1626: byang chub rdo rje rigs lnga lcam dral dang //
NK010(tha)004:1627: bde ba'i 'khor lo rig 'dzin rdo rje chos //
NK010(tha)004:1628: pra b+ha hasti sangs rgyas pad+ma skyes //
NK010(tha)004:1629: bstan pa'i chu 'go dgongs brda' snyan brgyud la //
NK010(tha)004:1630: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)004:1631: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)004:1632: bi ma la dang bal po many+dzu sh+r+ai //
NK010(tha)004:1633: rdo rje sems ma 'gar ston shes rab 'byung //
NK010(tha)004:1634: chos kyi rgyal po tshangs pa'i me tog sogs //
NK010(tha)004:1635: rgyal lugs brgyud pa'i bla ma thams cad la //
NK010(tha)004:1636: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)004:1637: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)004:1638: jo mo mkhar chen bza' dang cog ro bza' //
NK010(tha)004:1639: dpal gyi dbang phyug ngam 'bre a tsar sa //
NK010(tha)004:1640: smad las rtsal thon lag lhag byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)004:1641: jo lcam brgyud pa'i bla ma thams cad la //
NK010(tha)004:1642: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)004:1643: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)004:1644: rdo rje bdud 'joms a tsar dpal me tog /
NK010(tha)004:1645: rdo rje gzhon nu zhang zhung yon tan grags //
NK010(tha)004:1646: yon tan rin chen kun mkhyen rong zom sogs //
NK010(tha)004:1647: sna nam brgyud pa'i bla ma thams cad la //
NK010(tha)004:1648: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)004:1649: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)004:1650: phyi yul snang char dgra bgegs gnyis la thebs //
NK010(tha)004:1651: sems med 'byung ba chu yang chom la phob //
NK010(tha)004:1652: gnyags lo mchog dang lha dpal 'o bran sogs //
NK010(tha)004:1653: sham sngon brgyud pa'i bla ma thams cad la //
NK010(tha)004:1654: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)004:1655: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)004:1656: nang du rang rgyud nyon mongs dug lngar thebs //
NK010(tha)004:1657: mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pas mu stegs btul //
NK010(tha)004:1658: rnal 'byor dbang phyug 'dar phyar la sogs pa //
NK010(tha)004:1659: dpal chen phur pa'i grub thob thams cad la //
NK010(tha)004:1660: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)004:1661: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)004:1662: don dam byang chub sems kyi phur pa ni //
NK010(tha)004:1663: rtogs pa chos sku'i ngang nas dgongs brgyud dang //
NK010(tha)004:1664: rig 'dzin mkha' 'gro'i brda' las snyan brgyud rdzogs //
NK010(tha)004:1665: pad+mas lung bstan 'jigs med gling pa la //
NK010(tha)004:1666: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub bstsol //
NK010(tha)004:1667: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)004:1668: phrin las 'od zer 'jigs med chos kyi grags //
NK010(tha)004:1669: gzhan phan mtha' yas thub bstan rgyal mtshan dpal //
NK010(tha)004:1670: dpal ldan chos grags phan bde'i 'od zer zhabs //
NK010(tha)004:1671: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)004:1672: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)004:1673: kha skong sh+lo ka 'di dz+ny+aa nas so //
NK010(tha)004:1674: bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor yab yum dang //
NK010(tha)004:1675: sras mchog rigs lnga phur pa rdzas kyi lha //
NK010(tha)004:1676: phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor khra thabs dang //
NK010(tha)004:1677: dkyil 'khor mu ran skyong ba'i phur srung la //
NK010(tha)004:1678: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)004:1679: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)004:1680: mthar dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK010(tha)004:1681: rgyal ba'i ye shes gsang ba gsum //
NK010(tha)004:1683: rdo rje lce yi dam tshig gis //
NK010(tha)004:1684: myang pas dngos grub thob par gyur //
NK010(tha)004:1685: rang gi ya rkan la dkar po /
NK010(tha)004:1687: lce la h+aum gis mtshan pa dang so sor 'dres /
NK010(tha)004:1688: spyi mgrin snying ga gsum du song bas gnas so
NK010(tha)004:1689: sor sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum du gyur par
NK010(tha)004:1690: bsam mo // drug pa gtor ma'i mchod pa ni /
NK010(tha)004:1693: gti mug sha'i 'dod yon du bltas nas /
NK010(tha)004:1696: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK010(tha)004:1697: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK010(tha)004:1698: dpal chen 'khor bcas spyan drangs te //
NK010(tha)004:1699: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK010(tha)004:1700: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK010(tha)004:1701: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK010(tha)004:1703: ma lus gshegs nas rnams su gsol //
NK010(tha)004:1707: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)004:1708: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)004:1709: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)004:1710: dug gsum mchod par rab phul bas //
NK010(tha)004:1711: sangs rgyas sku gsum thob par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)004:1712: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK010(tha)004:1713: dzahmh'u bam hoh sarba big+h+n+aana bam h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:1714: ma h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa hi kha ram kh+aa hi kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)004:1715: bdun pa rak+ta'i mchod pa tshar gsum ni /
NK010(tha)004:1717: dang po pho nyal bka' bsgo ba'i phyir phul nas /
NK010(tha)004:1719: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)004:1720: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)004:1721: zung zhig rgyob cig rnam par chings //
NK010(tha)004:1722: gtogs shing grogs dang bral bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)004:1723: rengs par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK010(tha)004:1724: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK010(tha)004:1725: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK010(tha)004:1726: bsgo ba'i bka' 'di nyan par bya'o //
NK010(tha)004:1728: gnyis pa dam can gnad la dbab pa'i phyir dbul ba ni /
NK010(tha)004:1730: bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)004:1731: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK010(tha)004:1732: sngon chad ji bzhin bcas pa yis //
NK010(tha)004:1733: mngon spyod phrin las myur du mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:1735: gsum pa mthu dang rdzu 'phrul 'phrog pa'i ched du dbul ba ni /
NK010(tha)004:1737: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)004:1738: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)004:1740: nga la bar chad byed pa rnams //
NK010(tha)004:1741: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:1743: brgyad pa las kyi mtha' sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pas bsdu ba ni /
NK010(tha)004:1744: lag pa'i sor mo g.yas g.yon khrag 'thung yab yum lngar bsam ste sbyar /
NK010(tha)004:1745: yab mkha' h+aum las rdo rje me dpal dang /
NK010(tha)004:1746: yum mkha' e las gnam lcags kyi brub khung du
NK010(tha)004:1747: bsam pa'i nang du dgra bgegs bkug nas brdung bas
NK010(tha)004:1748: sbyor sgrol zung 'jug gi mchod pas mnyes par bsam
NK010(tha)004:1750: lag pa khrag 'thung yab yum bcus //
NK010(tha)004:1751: dug gsum rtsad nas bcad pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)004:1752: khams gsum yongs sgrol sbyor ba byas //
NK010(tha)004:1754: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK010(tha)004:1755: bka' las 'das byed sdig can rnams //
NK010(tha)004:1756: rdo rje me dbal snying bsreg nas //
NK010(tha)004:1757: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlogs //
NK010(tha)004:1758: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK010(tha)004:1759: rdo rje tho bas brdung byas nas //
NK010(tha)004:1760: lha yang rung ste bsgral bar gyis //
NK010(tha)004:1764: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)004:1768: dgu pa bdud rtsi gsang nan gyi mchod pa ni /
NK010(tha)004:1769: b+hany+dzara bdud rtsi'i rgyun lan gsum du phyar nas bzed
NK010(tha)004:1770: zhal du sbrengs shing dang pos lha tshogs rnams dgyes
NK010(tha)004:1771: pa bskyed / gnyis pa nyan thos rnams 'gog pa las bslangs /
NK010(tha)004:1772: gsum pas rang rgyal rnams gzhan don la bskul bar bsams la /
NK010(tha)004:1774: mi bskyod ye shes bde ba'i mchog dang ldan pa'i ro la bsnams su gsol //
NK010(tha)004:1775: a la la hoh byang chub sems dpa'i bde mchog de nyid 'gog pa rnams las bslang ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)004:1776: chags pa med pa'i bde mchog kun tu myang mdzad bzhes shing bsnams su gsol //
NK010(tha)004:1778: mchog tu gsang ba'i bde la rol zhing dam bcas 'jig rten sgrol //
NK010(tha)004:1779: byang chub skye gnas bde mchog dbyings las mi nyams dga' ba'i gar mdzod cig /
NK010(tha)004:1780: a la la hoh zhen cing chags pas mtha' la nyon mongs rno skams gzir ba yis //
NK010(tha)004:1781: myo nga bde bde mchog brgyad dang ldan pas thabs kyi sku la smre bar mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:1782: 'gro kun tshangs par spyod pa'i byang chub sgo mor lam ston cig /
NK010(tha)004:1783: bde mchog bdud rtsi khyad par med pa'i tshogs la bka' stsol cig /
NK010(tha)004:1784: a la la hoh bcu pa don dam bden pa'i mchod pa ni /
NK010(tha)004:1787: yang dag don gyi phur pa ni //
NK010(tha)004:1788: ma spangs ma bsgrubs btsal ba med //
NK010(tha)004:1789: ma bslad ma bcos bsgyur du med //
NK010(tha)004:1790: lta ba don dam rtogs pa la //
NK010(tha)004:1791: rol pa cir yang 'gag pa med //
NK010(tha)004:1792: de nyid rtogs na phur pa'i don //
NK010(tha)004:1793: don dam rtogs pas thugs dam bskang //
NK010(tha)004:1794: zhes ngo bo nyid med pa'i don la mnyam par bzhag go //
NK010(tha)004:1795: bcu gcig pa bstod pa la spyi dang bye brag gnyis las /
NK010(tha)004:1796: dang po ni gsang ba gsum gyi yon tan khyad par can dran pas /
NK010(tha)004:1800: pad kor khro la khros pa'i khro bo che //
NK010(tha)004:1801: sna tshogs du ma'i pad kor khro bo'i sprin //
NK010(tha)004:1802: 'bar ba rdor sems gcig las rin 'byung rnam par snang mtha' 'byung //
NK010(tha)004:1804: de bzhin skor phyag nyid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)004:1805: sna tshogs du ma'i gzugs mchog ni //
NK010(tha)004:1806: khro bo bcu yi rang bzhin che //
NK010(tha)004:1807: gcig ni du mar 'phel mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)004:1808: du ma rnams la bdag cag bstod //
NK010(tha)004:1809: kye ma khro bo'i sprin phung che //
NK010(tha)004:1810: mtha' yas sdig pa gsod mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)004:1811: mngon spyod sgrol ba'i rang bzhin las //
NK010(tha)004:1812: bdag gi sdig pa gsod par mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:1813: e ma dpa' bo dpa' bo che //
NK010(tha)004:1814: ma lus kun gyi rgyal po nyid //
NK010(tha)004:1815: snying rje khros pas khro bo che //
NK010(tha)004:1816: khams gsum rgyal po a la la //
NK010(tha)004:1817: e ma'o bsdigs pa'i sdigs mdzub can //
NK010(tha)004:1818: sdigs pa'i spyod la sogs pas brjid //
NK010(tha)004:1819: mngon spyod khyod kyi sku dang mtshams //
NK010(tha)004:1824: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK010(tha)004:1825: dgod dang gshe dang 'jigs par byed pa dang //
NK010(tha)004:1826: snying rje rngams zhi rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku //
NK010(tha)004:1827: zhe sdang 'joms pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK010(tha)004:1828: yab kyi thugs dam dgyes pa bskyed pa'i yum //
NK010(tha)004:1830: e ka dza ti zhe sdang 'joms mdzad ma //
NK010(tha)004:1831: 'dod chags tshul gyis 'dod chags 'joms la bstod //
NK010(tha)004:1833: ye shes lnga ldan phur bus dug lnga 'joms //
NK010(tha)004:1834: phrin las lnga yis dregs pa sgrol ba la //
NK010(tha)004:1835: thogs pa med pa'i las mdzad 'dus pa lnga //
NK010(tha)004:1836: sras mchog rigs lnga'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK010(tha)004:1837: ye shes rol pa'i stobs bcus mi dge 'joms //
NK010(tha)004:1838: sku gsung thugs kyis gdug pa sgrol bar mdzad //
NK010(tha)004:1839: yang dag don gyis log 'dren 'joms mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)004:1840: khro bo yab yum bcu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK010(tha)004:1841: byang chub bde la sgrol ba'i pho nya mo //
NK010(tha)004:1842: ye shes don la phra thabs gzugs 'dzin cing //
NK010(tha)004:1843: dregs pa'i tshogs rnams ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)004:1844: phra men pho nya'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK010(tha)004:1845: bcu gnyis pa rgyal ba dgyes byed dam baca'i mchod pa ni /
NK010(tha)004:1848: bskal pa dpag tu med pa tshun chod nas //
NK010(tha)004:1849: da lta'i lus 'di bskyed pa phan chad du //
NK010(tha)004:1850: lha mchog khyed dang smon lam mthu bsdebs nas //
NK010(tha)004:1851: dus 'dir zhal mthong yi dam lhar gsol na //
NK010(tha)004:1852: dus tshigs 'di nas bzung nas yi dam lha //
NK010(tha)004:1853: snying po byang chub mchog la mi gnas tshun //
NK010(tha)004:1854: tshe rabs 'khor ba gar byung gar skyes kyang //
NK010(tha)004:1855: gsang ba'i lha mchog khyed dang mi 'bral zhing //
NK010(tha)004:1856: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig las //
NK010(tha)004:1857: mi 'da' ba dang yun du bdag bsrung gis //
NK010(tha)004:1858: chad lhag 'gal 'khrul mchis na mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)004:1859: bar chod rkyen gyis rnam smin ci byung yang //
NK010(tha)004:1860: dpal chen khyod kyi mod la zil gyis gnon //
NK010(tha)004:1861: dngos grub mchog stsol shes rab lha mo'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)004:1862: gnyis pa ye shes kyi tshogs bsags dzapa kyi rim pa la bzhi las /
NK010(tha)004:1863: dang po dzapa khang dbye ba ni /
NK010(tha)004:1864: snang cha ma lus pa dbye gzhi'i dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum du rdzogs par byas nas /
NK010(tha)004:1865: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he phata dzah badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya d+aip+ta tsakra h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:1866: ces bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK010(tha)004:1867: bud+d+ha badz+ra rat+na pad+ma karma k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK010(tha)004:1868: ces sras mchog rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK010(tha)004:1879: dzahdzah dzahmh'u bam hoh phata dzah zhes pas phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor te /
NK010(tha)004:1880: dkyil 'khor gsum ldan gyi dam tshig gi 'khor lo
NK010(tha)004:1881: las ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor rten dang brten par
NK010(tha)004:1882: bcas pa logs su phye nas /
NK010(tha)004:1883: mdun gyi nam mkhar me ri 'dab 'byor gyi tshul du yod par bsam mo //
NK010(tha)004:1886: thugs kar dpal gyi be'u'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK010(tha)004:1887: sgo gcig rin chen gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)004:1888: bde stong dbyer med ngang nyid las //
NK010(tha)004:1889: chos kyi sku las longs skur shar //
NK010(tha)004:1890: pad+ma zla ba'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK010(tha)004:1891: skyon gyis ma gos gti mug sel //
NK010(tha)004:1892: yab yum gnyis med zag med sku //
NK010(tha)004:1893: sku mdog dkar gsal rnam dag dbyings //
NK010(tha)004:1894: rdo rje dril bu phyag na bsnams //
NK010(tha)004:1895: shes rab byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)004:1896: rtog med mi 'gyur skyil krung bzhugs //
NK010(tha)004:1897: mkha' dbyings bde chen sku la bstod //
NK010(tha)004:1898: ces brjod nas bdag mdun gyi gtso bo'i thugs kar
NK010(tha)004:1899: ye shes sems dpa' zhi ba longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK010(tha)004:1900: sku yum dang bcas pa'i thugs kar de bzhin gshegs
NK010(tha)004:1901: pa thams cad kyi thugs rdo rje'i ngo bo rdo
NK010(tha)004:1902: rje mthing nag rtse lnga dang /
NK010(tha)004:1903: de'i lte bar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng ting
NK010(tha)004:1904: 'dzin sems dpa' h'u mthing nag la 'bru dgu'i sngags
NK010(tha)004:1907: snying gar bsam par bya ba ni //
NK010(tha)004:1908: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor dbus gnas par //
NK010(tha)004:1909: rdo rje sa bon mthing nag bzhag /
NK010(tha)004:1910: snying po brtag par bya ba ni //
NK010(tha)004:1911: rnam par snang mdzad mgor bzhag ste //
NK010(tha)004:1912: rdo rje phur bu'i rang bzhin brtag /
NK010(tha)004:1914: gsum pa dzapa dngos la gnyis /
NK010(tha)004:1915: stod las la brten nas bla na med pa'i byang chub bsgrub pa dang /
NK010(tha)004:1916: smad las la brten nas dam can nye bar bsnyen pa'o //
NK010(tha)004:1917: dang po la bsnyen bsgrub yan lag bzhi'i nges pa
NK010(tha)004:1918: yang mtha' gcig tu ma nges te thabs bskyed pa'i
NK010(tha)004:1919: rim pa la sbyar ma thag pas kyang shes shing
NK010(tha)004:1920: / phur pa rnal 'byor chen po las kyang /
NK010(tha)004:1921: spyir ni gsang sngags nges pa la //
NK010(tha)004:1922: ting 'dzin gsum bskyed bsnyen pa yin //
NK010(tha)004:1923: bdag nyid lhar bskyed nye bsnyen yin //
NK010(tha)004:1924: yum bskyed bsgrub par shes par bya //
NK010(tha)004:1925: gzhan rnams bsgrub pa chen po yin //
NK010(tha)004:1927: 'di ni stod las byang chub sgrub pa'i gnas skabs
NK010(tha)004:1928: na bsnyen sgrub gnyis la nang gses kyis yan lag
NK010(tha)004:1929: bzhir phye na chos nyid dang sbyar te bzla ba
NK010(tha)004:1930: bsnyen pa / lha dang sbyar te bzla ba nye bsnyen /
NK010(tha)004:1931: sham bur sbyar ba sgrub pa /
NK010(tha)004:1932: tshogs sgrub dang 'brel ba'am phrin las sna tshogs pa can sgrub pa chen por nges pa las /
NK010(tha)004:1934: 'dir sgrub pa zhag bdun la mtshon na nyin dang po gsum la bsnyen sngags /
NK010(tha)004:1935: badz+ra k+ai li ki la ya h'u /
NK010(tha)004:1937: nyin bar ma gsum la sarba big nan bam sogs btags pa nye bsnyen /
NK010(tha)004:1938: nyin phyi ma gcig la sgrub sngags dzahmh'u a gsum bag shes par bya'o //
NK010(tha)004:1941: bdag mdun so so'i dkyil 'khor rten dang brten pa
NK010(tha)004:1942: sems dpa' sum brtsegs sngags phreng dang bcas pa'i lhar
NK010(tha)004:1943: snang dang lhan cig 'bru dgu pa'i bzlas pa la
NK010(tha)004:1944: brtson pa bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK010(tha)004:1945: skyo ba'i tshe chos nyid dang sbyar nas bzla ba ye shees kyi tshogs dang 'brel ba yin te /
NK010(tha)004:1947: lha yi nga rgyal rab gnas pa //
NK010(tha)004:1948: brjed pa med pa'i dran pa ni //
NK010(tha)004:1949: 'bad pa med pa'i tshogs chen po //
NK010(tha)004:1950: mkhal pas rtag tu bsam par bya //
NK010(tha)004:1953: lha nyid bsgom dang spyan drang yang //
NK010(tha)004:1954: gzhi rtsa med par ma shes na //
NK010(tha)004:1955: lha nyid brtags pas log rtog nyid //
NK010(tha)004:1956: gzhi rtsa med par lha bsgoms pas //
NK010(tha)004:1957: chos nyid don dam rtogs pa dang //
NK010(tha)004:1958: log pa'i chos can 'dul ba dang //
NK010(tha)004:1959: 'gro ba tha dad drangs pa dang //
NK010(tha)004:1960: bdud dang srin po dbang du sdud //
NK010(tha)004:1961: dper na me long snang gzhi la //
NK010(tha)004:1962: gzhi rtsa med pas thams cad snang //
NK010(tha)004:1963: ma bltas stong la rnam par snang //
NK010(tha)004:1964: yod dang med pa'i dmigs dang bral //
NK010(tha)004:1965: zhes pa'i don khong du chud par bya ba ni gal po che'o //
NK010(tha)004:1966: de la gsal brtan cung zad thob nas 'od zer spro bsdu bya ba ni /
NK010(tha)004:1967: thugs srog ting 'dzin sems dpa' las 'od zer bung
NK010(tha)004:1968: ba'i mtshon cha lta bu 'phros sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK010(tha)004:1969: khams thams cad g.yos shing mnyes pa'i mchod pa phul
NK010(tha)004:1970: / sems can gyi khams la 'phros pas sdig sgrib sbyangs /
NK010(tha)004:1971: dag pa'i snod bcud 'ba' zhig tu gyur pas don gnyis byas /
NK010(tha)004:1972: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK010(tha)004:1973: kyi byin rlabs sku dang yig 'bru phyag mtshan gyi
NK010(tha)004:1974: rnam par byung ste bdag mdun gyi dkyil 'khor la
NK010(tha)004:1975: thim pas byin rlabs dang dngos grub mtha' dag thob
NK010(tha)004:1976: par bsam mo // de la cung zad goms pa dang do li la bslab par bya ste /
NK010(tha)004:1977: sngags phreng las rang 'dra gnyis pa re chad pa lu gu rgyud du 'brel /
NK010(tha)004:1978: rdo rje'i dbus su nas thon ye shes sems dpa'i sku'i dbyibs brgyud zhal du thon /
NK010(tha)004:1979: rim bzhin bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi shangs bug g.yas pa las thon /
NK010(tha)004:1980: rdo rje gzhon nu ye shes pa'i shangs bug g.yon
NK010(tha)004:1981: nas zhugs te thugs kar thim sku gsung thugs mnyes
NK010(tha)004:1984: de'i shangs bug g.yas nas brgyud rang gi sna bug g.yon du zhugs /
NK010(tha)004:1985: rim par brgyud pas bdag mdun gyi rten dang brten pa thams cad shin tu gsal bar byas /
NK010(tha)004:1988: dngos grub rnam pa gnyis bde blag tu thob par
NK010(tha)004:1989: bsam pa las rnam rtog gzhan gyis bar ma chod
NK010(tha)004:1990: par bya ste / phur pa gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK010(tha)004:1991: rig pa byang chub sems nyid rtogs nas kyang //
NK010(tha)004:1992: rang bzhin ma skyes yongs su grub pa'i sku //
NK010(tha)004:1993: snang ba rang bzhin med de 'ja' tshon 'dra //
NK010(tha)004:1994: chu zla lta bu'i sangs rgyas 'od dang ldan //
NK010(tha)004:1995: thugs kar dpal be'ura yi ge 'bru dgu ni //
NK010(tha)004:1996: gser la phra bkod bzhin du gsal bsgom ste //
NK010(tha)004:1997: rdzogs pa'i rim pa gdams ngag tshul bzhin bsgom //
NK010(tha)004:1998: rgod na skye med rmugs na chos nyid la //
NK010(tha)004:1999: 'phro na bde chen byings na khro bo ste //
NK010(tha)004:2000: ye shes lha yi bsnyen pa'i ting nge 'dzin //
NK010(tha)004:2001: 'dzab kyi dgongs pa chu bo'i rgyun bzhin no //
NK010(tha)004:2002: chos nyid ngang las sngags kyi sgra dbyangs blangs //
NK010(tha)004:2003: sems 'dzin bsam gtan ting 'dzin ma yengs bsgom //
NK010(tha)004:2004: dbyings kyi ngang las rang byung rang grags bsam //
NK010(tha)004:2005: de tshe rnam rtog dgra chen thams cad kun //
NK010(tha)004:2006: gzung 'dzin mtshan ma med pa'i dbyings su phur //
NK010(tha)004:2009: sde tshan bcu bzhi pa la bya ste /
NK010(tha)004:2010: 'di ni bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags brgyad po la
NK010(tha)004:2011: bskul ba las kyi sngags dang bzlas pa las kyi
NK010(tha)004:2012: 'bru gsum bsnan pa thams cad 'dus pa'i drag sngags
NK010(tha)004:2014: +amo ni dpal chen yab yin te //
NK010(tha)004:2015: badz+ra shes rab yum yin no //
NK010(tha)004:2016: k+ai ni ye shes khro bo la //
NK010(tha)004:2017: li ni dbyings kyi khro mo bcu //
NK010(tha)004:2018: k+ai ni thabs kyi mche ba can //
NK010(tha)004:2019: la ni shes rab gshog pa can //
NK010(tha)004:2020: ya ni sras mchog phur pa ste //
NK010(tha)004:2021: h+aum ni phyag brnyan sgo ma bzhi //
NK010(tha)004:2023: big ni dgra dang bgegs yin te //
NK010(tha)004:2024: nan ni dgra dang bgegs mnan no //
NK010(tha)004:2025: bam ni dbang du sdud pa ste //
NK010(tha)004:2026: h'u ni brlag par byed pa'o //
NK010(tha)004:2027: phata kyis sgrol ba'i phrin las mdzad //
NK010(tha)004:2031: sa ya drug 'bum bsnyen pa'i tshad //
NK010(tha)004:2032: ces pa'i 'bum phrag bcu drug go //
NK010(tha)004:2033: sde tshan bcu bzhi pa 'di ni las rung tsam
NK010(tha)004:2034: gyi bsnyen tshad de smin bar slob pa'i bsnyen tshad
NK010(tha)004:2035: la 'bum phrag brgya tham pa ste bshad ma thag
NK010(tha)004:2037: bye ba sngon la 'dren pa snga 'gyur gyi khyad
NK010(tha)004:2038: chos su 'dod pa'ang nor ba chen po yin te
NK010(tha)004:2039: k+ai la bcu gnyis kyi tan+t+ra chung ba las /
NK010(tha)004:2040: rdo rje phur pa lha bskyed bya //
NK010(tha)004:2042: bye ba bzlas te dbang bskur nas //
NK010(tha)004:2043: zhes pas dus kyi 'khor lo dang mtshungs pa yin no //
NK010(tha)004:2045: dzahmh'u +aahgasuma bsnan pa'i bcu bdun te /
NK010(tha)004:2046: dang pos dngos grub thams cad sngags la sdud /
NK010(tha)004:2047: gnyis pas sngags kyi dngos grub bdag la sdud /
NK010(tha)004:2048: gsum pas rang bzhin dbyer med du rgyas 'debs pa'i man ngag gi lde kha khyad par can no //
NK010(tha)004:2049: bzhi pa sgrub pa chen po ni dkyil 'khor gyi bya ba dang 'brel ba dang /
NK010(tha)004:2051: bum sgrub la sogs pa dang /
NK010(tha)004:2052: gzhan yang phrin las sna tshogs pa'i bdag nyid de /
NK010(tha)004:2053: phur par rang gzhung du ye shes lha yi sgrub pa /
NK010(tha)004:2055: dpa' bo ging gi sgrub pa zhes smad las kyi
NK010(tha)004:2056: rim pa sgrub pa chen por bsdu ba yang yod
NK010(tha)004:2057: do // de dag gi bar skabs ci rigs par
NK010(tha)004:2058: dag pa'i snod bcud la gsal brtan gyi ye shes
NK010(tha)004:2059: bskyed phyir dzapa bskul bya bar spro na /
NK010(tha)004:2061: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK010(tha)004:2062: sogs rgyud las gsungs pa dngos zur du bkod pa ltar bya'o //
NK010(tha)004:2063: so so'i sngags dang dmigs pa'i khyad par zab mo
NK010(tha)004:2064: ni rtsod dus 'di na sngags la 'phya zhing dam
NK010(tha)004:2065: tshig med pa'i gang zag mang bas dngos grub kyi
NK010(tha)004:2066: gnas la zhud pa'i phyir re zhig dpa' bo mkha'
NK010(tha)004:2067: 'gro'i bka' rgyas chu 'babs su bri bar ma gnang
NK010(tha)004:2068: ngo // de ltar yang dngos grub kyi rgyu dam
NK010(tha)004:2069: tshig ma nyams pa rnams la ni mchog dang thun
NK010(tha)004:2070: mong gi dngos grub tshang la ma nor ba grub
NK010(tha)004:2071: pa'i rgyud gzhung 'di nyid kyis ston pas na /
NK010(tha)004:2072: gang zhig bsgrub pa'i phan yon la bsams nas yid
NK010(tha)004:2073: bzhin gyi nor bu lta bur bzung bar rigs te
NK010(tha)004:2074: / rdo rje khros pa'i rtsa bshad las /
NK010(tha)004:2075: 'di la brten pa'i gang zag rnams //
NK010(tha)004:2076: thams cad grol 'gyur the tshom med //
NK010(tha)004:2077: rdo rje khrag 'thung nga nyid kyi //
NK010(tha)004:2078: yi ge h'u tsam bzlas pa yang //
NK010(tha)004:2079: bar chad bdud kyis mi tshugs shing //
NK010(tha)004:2080: mtshan ma grub par the tshom med //
NK010(tha)004:2081: rdo rje can gyi zhing du skye //
NK010(tha)004:2082: lha klu kun la dbang byed 'gyur //
NK010(tha)004:2083: 'di bsgrub pa yi gang zag rnams //
NK010(tha)004:2084: snga nas sbyong bar the tshom med //
NK010(tha)004:2085: tshe gcig 'di la brtson ldan pas //
NK010(tha)004:2086: 'khor bar mi ldog mngon sangs rgyas //
NK010(tha)004:2087: gang zhig dbang dang man ngag thob //
NK010(tha)004:2088: skad cig tsam gyis mos gyur na //
NK010(tha)004:2089: 'chi ba zhes ni rnam rtog ste //
NK010(tha)004:2091: gang zhig 'di la mos pa tsam //
NK010(tha)004:2092: dbang dang dam tshig 'dzin gyur nas //
NK010(tha)004:2093: skye bdun nyid na sangs rgyas 'gyur //
NK010(tha)004:2094: skye ba gzhan gyis bar ma chod //
NK010(tha)004:2095: 'di la the tshom le lo spangs //
NK010(tha)004:2096: brtson 'grus dad ldan can gyis bsgrub //
NK010(tha)004:2097: rgyud 'di rtag tu gsang bar bya //
NK010(tha)004:2100: bzhi pa dzapa mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK010(tha)004:2101: mchod bstod rgyas bsdus ci rigs pa'i mthar yi ge brgya pa lan gsum gyi nongs bshags dang /
NK010(tha)004:2102: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dbyer med du bya ba'i phyir /
NK010(tha)004:2103: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h'u /
NK010(tha)004:2104: zhes rig pa'i me tog dor /
NK010(tha)004:2105: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK010(tha)004:2106: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya phata /
NK010(tha)004:2107: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya ho /
NK010(tha)004:2108: zhes pas dngos grub bskul nas /
NK010(tha)004:2110: mdun bskyed ye shes kyi 'khor lo dam tshig gi 'khor lo la dbyer med du bstim /
NK010(tha)004:2112: ces brjod nas de nyid gsal zhing brtan par bya'o //
NK010(tha)004:2113: gnyis pa smad las kyi dang po dam can nye bar bsnyen pa ni zur du 'chad la /
NK010(tha)004:2114: ngan sngags nye bar bsnyen pa gdab pa drug gis
NK010(tha)004:2115: dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i skor ni byang chub sems dpa'i
NK010(tha)004:2116: tshul khrims sngags sdom dang sbyar ba'i gnang bkag mi
NK010(tha)004:2117: shes pa dag gis gsang sngags kyi phrin las rab
NK010(tha)004:2118: 'byams rang gar spyad pas ngan song du 'phen pa'i
NK010(tha)004:2119: tshul mang du mthong bas bdag cag ni byang chub
NK010(tha)004:2120: sems dpa'i sde snod la dad pas mngon spyod kyi
NK010(tha)004:2121: las la brtson pa lhod par gyur to //
NK010(tha)004:2122: de ltar yang zhib tu shes par 'dod pa'i dam
NK010(tha)004:2123: tshig can yod na phur pa rnal 'byor chen po'i
NK010(tha)004:2124: rgyud dang 'brel ba'i don sna nam lugs kyi rnam
NK010(tha)004:2125: bshad rin chen phreng ba dang /
NK010(tha)004:2127: 'bum 'grel la sogs las shes par bya'o //
NK010(tha)004:2128: rjes la tshogs kyi rim pa ni /
NK010(tha)004:2130: dpal chen thugs las ram yam kham //
NK010(tha)004:2132: snang srid bde chen ka p+aa lar //
NK010(tha)004:2133: bcud rnams rigs lnga'i dam rdzas gyur //
NK010(tha)004:2136: 'og min chos dbyings pho brang dang //
NK010(tha)004:2137: yan lag bdun ldan longs spyod rdzogs //
NK010(tha)004:2138: rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing khams nas //
NK010(tha)004:2139: dpal chen dkyil 'khor lha tshogs dang //
NK010(tha)004:2140: gnas dang nye gnas rnam pa gnyis //
NK010(tha)004:2141: yul ni rol pa nye yul rol //
NK010(tha)004:2142: zhing dang nye ba'i zhing dang ni //
NK010(tha)004:2145: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK010(tha)004:2146: dur khrod chen po bsil ba'i tshal //
NK010(tha)004:2147: oo di ya nar pad+ma brtsegs //
NK010(tha)004:2148: za hor yul na khu byug klong //
NK010(tha)004:2149: seng nga'i yul na sku la rdzogs //
NK010(tha)004:2150: kha che'i yul na he chen rol //
NK010(tha)004:2151: bal po'i yul na ya ma kha //
NK010(tha)004:2152: tho gar yul na gsang chen rol //
NK010(tha)004:2153: li yul 'jig rten mngon rdzogs te //
NK010(tha)004:2154: dur khrod chen po brgyad rnams na //
NK010(tha)004:2155: bzhugs pa'i dpa' bo mkha' 'gro dang //
NK010(tha)004:2157: tshogs la spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol //
NK010(tha)004:2158: tshogs khang 'di ni sprul pa'i zhing //
NK010(tha)004:2159: tshogs rdzas 'dod yon rol pa'i rgyan //
NK010(tha)004:2160: thabs dang shes rab lcam dral ldan //
NK010(tha)004:2161: rdo rje'i glu gar byin re chags //
NK010(tha)004:2162: cang te'u dril bu snyan zhing 'khrol //
NK010(tha)004:2163: 'di ni dam tshig mchog gi gnas /
NK010(tha)004:2164: shags dang rtsod pa ku co med //
NK010(tha)004:2165: rig pa brtul zhugs nyams dang ldan //
NK010(tha)004:2166: dam tshig 'di ni dang du bzhes //
NK010(tha)004:2167: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)004:2168: gu ru d+he wa d+aa ka d+aa ki n+ai d+har+m+aa
NK010(tha)004:2169: p+aa la sa ma ya dzah phud dang po ni
NK010(tha)004:2171: sangs rgyas dam tshig bla na med //
NK010(tha)004:2172: sha lnga bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga //
NK010(tha)004:2173: bza' bca' btung ba phyi yi tshogs //
NK010(tha)004:2174: 'dod yon lha mo rnam pa lnga //
NK010(tha)004:2175: dbang po'i longs spyod nang gi tshogs //
NK010(tha)004:2176: bde stong ye shes bla na med //
NK010(tha)004:2177: dga' bzhi rnam rol gsang ba'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)004:2179: bzhes nas dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)004:2180: ga na tsakra p+au dza hoh bar pa bshags pa ni /
NK010(tha)004:2182: gang zhig 'khrul par gyur pa de nas bzung //
NK010(tha)004:2183: rnam smin lus la brten pa de srid du //
NK010(tha)004:2184: mi dge bcu dang mtshams med nye ba lnga //
NK010(tha)004:2185: lci ba bcu drug log pa brgyad la sogs //
NK010(tha)004:2186: theg pa gsum dang rig pa 'dzin pa yi //
NK010(tha)004:2187: sdom gsum dam tshig nyams pa mtha' dag kun //
NK010(tha)004:2188: ga na tshogs kyi 'khor lo la brten nas //
NK010(tha)004:2189: 'chab pa med pa'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)004:2190: dag tshangs chen po'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK010(tha)004:2191: he ru ka'i yig brgya bazla'o //
NK010(tha)004:2193: e las thar med srid pa'i brub khung nang //
NK010(tha)004:2194: ma rig 'khrul pas bcings pa bdag lta'i dgra //
NK010(tha)004:2195: ye shes dbyings la sgrib pa'i gzung 'dzin bgegs //
NK010(tha)004:2196: dag chen ye shes rig pa'i lcags kyus zungs //
NK010(tha)004:2197: mnyam par ma bzhag med pa'i zhags pas chings //
NK010(tha)004:2198: lhag mthong lu gu rgyud kyi d+r+wa bas sdoms //
NK010(tha)004:2199: rjes thob 'khrul pa med pa'i dril bus myos //
NK010(tha)004:2200: phung po lnga yi nye bar len pa kun //
NK010(tha)004:2201: bdag med rtogs pa'i mtshon gyis rnam par gtub //
NK010(tha)004:2202: skye med khros pa'i lha tshogs zhal du bstab //
NK010(tha)004:2203: m+aam sa rak+ta tsit+ta go ro tsa na ba su
NK010(tha)004:2204: ta kim ni ri ti ta na tsakra p+au dza
NK010(tha)004:2205: kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)004:2207: zhing lpags kyi steng du bzhag la /
NK010(tha)004:2208: he ru ka'i dam rgyas kha phru dbab /
NK010(tha)004:2212: dang po phud kyis mi mchod du //
NK010(tha)004:2213: dpal chen dkyil 'khor tshogs kyi bdag /
NK010(tha)004:2214: bar du bshags pa mi bgyi ru //
NK010(tha)004:2215: rnal 'byor ldan pa dam tshig gnyan //
NK010(tha)004:2216: tha ma bsgral bstab mi bgyi ru //
NK010(tha)004:2217: rtogs pas bdag rgyud sngon bsgral phyir //
NK010(tha)004:2218: da lta lhag mas mi mchod du //
NK010(tha)004:2219: ma tshogs dbang phyug ging lang+ka //
NK010(tha)004:2220: pho nya sum brgya drug cu sogs //
NK010(tha)004:2221: kun kyang dpal chen sprul pa yin //
NK010(tha)004:2222: lhag ma kha chus mi bran du //
NK010(tha)004:2223: dam tshig gcig tu bsre ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)004:2224: 'bangs thog rje yis mi mnan du //
NK010(tha)004:2225: ci bcol las la bskul ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)004:2226: rje la 'bangs kyis mi rgol du //
NK010(tha)004:2227: drag shul las thabs myur ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)004:2229: rnam dag rang bzhin zhi ba las //
NK010(tha)004:2230: bcom ldan dpal chen sprul pa ni //
NK010(tha)004:2231: thabs shes zla gsang rol pa las //
NK010(tha)004:2232: dkyil 'khor mu ran skyong ba ste //
NK010(tha)004:2233: khyed cag sngon gyi yal gam can //
NK010(tha)004:2234: lag na glo snying nang khrol thogs //
NK010(tha)004:2235: legs nyes stangs 'dzin tshogs khang nyul //
NK010(tha)004:2236: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul dpag tu med //
NK010(tha)004:2237: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kas //
NK010(tha)004:2238: dug gsum r+au tra bsgral ba'i tshe //
NK010(tha)004:2239: khas blangs dam bcas dran gyis la //
NK010(tha)004:2240: srin mo'i za lam chen po ru //
NK010(tha)004:2241: pham phabs long la bstan pa srungs //
NK010(tha)004:2242: bcol ba'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:2245: mi gnas ye shes chos sku'i pho brang nas //
NK010(tha)004:2246: longs spyod rdzogs pa zhi dang khro bo'i lha //
NK010(tha)004:2247: thugs dam bskul lo 'gro ba'i don la dgongs //
NK010(tha)004:2248: rig pa'i rang bzhin bde gshegs snying po yang //
NK010(tha)004:2249: ma rig 'dzin pa'i kun gzhi lung ma bstan //
NK010(tha)004:2250: sgo lnga'i yul dang rten cing 'brel ba las //
NK010(tha)004:2251: rigs drug rgyud lnga'i gnas su 'khyams pa rnams //
NK010(tha)004:2252: las dang nyon mongs mthu yis gzir ba'i mthu //
NK010(tha)004:2253: phyi rol yul la smin pa'i sdug bsngal dang //
NK010(tha)004:2254: nad mtshon mu ge dgra bgegs 'byung po'i gdon //
NK010(tha)004:2255: 'jigs pa chen po brgyad dang bcu drug kun //
NK010(tha)004:2256: mngon spyod drag po'i rol pas tshar bcad nas //
NK010(tha)004:2257: log rtog dngos por zhen pa'i sems can rnams //
NK010(tha)004:2258: rgyu 'bras theg pa gzhan gyis gdul dka' bas //
NK010(tha)004:2259: rang byung ye shes rtogs pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:2262: dus gsum rnam dag kun tu bzang po'i dus //
NK010(tha)004:2263: mngon rdzogs ye shes dam pa'i 'og min du //
NK010(tha)004:2264: kun gzhi yid chos dag pa'i ston pa yis //
NK010(tha)004:2265: rang snang rang bzhin med pa'i 'khor tshogs la //
NK010(tha)004:2266: rgyal ba dgongs brgyud rdzogs pa'i yo ga gsum //
NK010(tha)004:2267: brda' tshig brjod pa bral bar bstan pa'i tshe //
NK010(tha)004:2268: grags chen gsal ba'i ston pa bcu gnyis dang //
NK010(tha)004:2269: dga' rab dpa' bo gsang 'dzin rdo rje chos //
NK010(tha)004:2270: brda' brgyud rig 'dzin grub pa mchog rnams kyis //
NK010(tha)004:2271: ston 'khor dgongs pa gcig pa'i dbang thob bzhin //
NK010(tha)004:2272: tshogs brgyad rang grol gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK010(tha)004:2273: 'khrul pa gzhi la dag pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:2274: de rjes gsang sngags bstan pa byung ba'i tshe //
NK010(tha)004:2275: 'og min dga' ldan ri rab lhun po'i rtse //
NK010(tha)004:2276: lha gnas gsum du grags pa'i gnas mchog dang //
NK010(tha)004:2277: sham b+ha la dang o rgyan za hor yul //
NK010(tha)004:2278: sing ga la dang gnam lcags 'bar ba'i rtser //
NK010(tha)004:2279: mchod rten chen po bde byed brtsegs pa ru //
NK010(tha)004:2280: rig 'dzin sde snod mtha' dag bab pa'i tshe //
NK010(tha)004:2282: dkyil 'khor mu ran skyong ba thams cad kyis //
NK010(tha)004:2283: gtor ma len zhing legs nyes stangs 'dzin pa'i //
NK010(tha)004:2284: khas blangs dam bca' bzhin du phrin las mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:2285: de rjes 'gro don dus la bab pa'i tshe //
NK010(tha)004:2286: klu sgrub snying po pad+ma thod phreng sogs //
NK010(tha)004:2287: grub pa'i rig 'dzin chen po brgyad rnams kyis //
NK010(tha)004:2288: 'dzam bu'i gling du dar zhing rgyas mdzad cing //
NK010(tha)004:2289: khyad par brag dmar dpal gyi mchims phu ru //
NK010(tha)004:2290: rig 'dzin slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis //
NK010(tha)004:2291: lha sras rgyal po tshangs pa'i me tog la //
NK010(tha)004:2292: sgrub pa bka' brgyad dkyil 'khor zhal phye zhing //
NK010(tha)004:2293: seng ge rnam rol khas bu ri yi rtser //
NK010(tha)004:2294: gnod sbyin thams cad dam la bzhag pa'i tshe //
NK010(tha)004:2295: srog snying phul te chad tho bzung ba ltar //
NK010(tha)004:2296: mchod gtor bzhes la phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:2297: de rjes tshogs bdun rol pa bal po'i yul //
NK010(tha)004:2298: rang snang mchod rten bya rung kha shor du //
NK010(tha)004:2299: rang byung rdo rje 'jigs med gling pa la //
NK010(tha)004:2300: dbyings kyi mkha' 'gros nam mkha' mdzod kyi brda' //
NK010(tha)004:2301: ye shes lnga ldan sprul pa'i shog ser las //
NK010(tha)004:2302: brag dmar bre gu brtsegs pa'i dge'u ru //
NK010(tha)004:2303: kun tu bzang po dri med 'od zer gyis //
NK010(tha)004:2304: bka' rgya lung rdzogs gtad rgya bkrol ba'i tshe //
NK010(tha)004:2305: spyan gcig khrag tu khol ba'i ma mo dang //
NK010(tha)004:2306: bya rog gtsug phud 'dzin pa'i drang srong gis //
NK010(tha)004:2307: khas blangs tha tshig bzhin du phrin las mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:2308: bshal chu gtor mar bran la brtan ma bskyang ba ni /
NK010(tha)004:2310: tshogs bdag bka' yi bdag nyid ni //
NK010(tha)004:2311: khrag 'thung rdo rje nam mkha'i yum //
NK010(tha)004:2312: gangs ri can gyi yul lha ni //
NK010(tha)004:2313: bdud dang gnod sbyin sman mo bzhi //
NK010(tha)004:2314: tshur spyon tshur spyon gtor ma longs //
NK010(tha)004:2315: rten 'brel yan lag bcu gnyis dang //
NK010(tha)004:2316: dus sbyor bcu gnyis gnas dag pas //
NK010(tha)004:2317: bal bod mtshams na tshe ring ma //
NK010(tha)004:2318: la stod rdo rje g.ya' ma skyong //
NK010(tha)004:2319: gnod sbyin gangs la kun bzang mo //
NK010(tha)004:2321: jo mo gangs rar spyan gcig ma //
NK010(tha)004:2322: byang na mkha' lding klu mo rgyal //
NK010(tha)004:2323: kha rag rdo rje khyung btsun ma //
NK010(tha)004:2324: rma chen spom rar drag mo rgyal //
NK010(tha)004:2325: kong btsun de mo bod khams skyong //
NK010(tha)004:2326: 'brog btsan rdo rje sman gcig ma //
NK010(tha)004:2327: jo mo nags rgyal g.ya' mo bsil //
NK010(tha)004:2328: dbus na rdo rje zu le sman //
NK010(tha)004:2329: kun kyang pad+ma'i bka' nyan te //
NK010(tha)004:2330: dam la gnas shing rigs la 'go //
NK010(tha)004:2331: tha tshig bzhin du gtor ma longs //
NK010(tha)004:2333: mu stegs 'gyu ba'i sgo phrang dang //
NK010(tha)004:2334: 'gong po spun dgu'i nad dal srungs //
NK010(tha)004:2335: rtag chad thar par 'khrul ba yi //
NK010(tha)004:2336: 'jig tshogs lta ba dbu mar bzlog /
NK010(tha)004:2337: bden don rnam pa bcu gnyis kyi //
NK010(tha)004:2338: bstan pa dar ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK010(tha)004:2342: te te kha rak+ma ma ma sring 'gro ma h'u b+h+yo h'u h'u /
NK010(tha)004:2343: gtor gzhong ri rab tu bsam pa kha sbub la /
NK010(tha)004:2345: dam sri bya ba'i sdig can khyod //
NK010(tha)004:2346: 'gro ba yongs kyi rgyud la rgol //
NK010(tha)004:2347: byang chub sems kyi brtul zhugs bros //
NK010(tha)004:2348: mnan no stong chen 'og tu mnan //
NK010(tha)004:2349: gtad do chu srin gre bar gtad //
NK010(tha)004:2350: bskyur ro gshin rje'i kha ru bskyur //
NK010(tha)004:2351: bsreg go ye shes me yis sreg /
NK010(tha)004:2352: bdag tu lta ba ma zhig bar //
NK010(tha)004:2353: bskal pa zhig kyang mi btang ngo //
NK010(tha)004:2355: de nas dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK010(tha)004:2356: sngar bzhin mchod cing bstod la /
NK010(tha)004:2358: byin rlabs kun gyi rtsa ba bla ma ni //
NK010(tha)004:2359: dngos grub stsol phyir dpal chen rol pa'i lha //
NK010(tha)004:2360: rnam thar sgo gsum thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK010(tha)004:2361: rang bzhin yongs grub byang chub sems kyi dngos //
NK010(tha)004:2362: phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)004:2363: sa bcu lam lnga dbang bcu phyi nang gnyis //
NK010(tha)004:2364: rig 'dzin bzhi dang sku lnga ye shes lnga //
NK010(tha)004:2365: grub chen brgyad dang phrin las rnam pa bzhi //
NK010(tha)004:2366: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin glo bur sgrib pa gnyis //
NK010(tha)004:2367: kun gzhi'i khams la bag la nyal gyi tshul //
NK010(tha)004:2368: shin tu rnam dag rnam kun mchog ldan gyi //
NK010(tha)004:2369: dngos grub dam pa deng 'dir stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)004:2375: zhes sgrub rdzas gnas gsum du gtugs shing myang ngo //
NK010(tha)004:2376: slar yang gtang rag gi mchod bstod phul la /
NK010(tha)004:2378: hoh sngags kyi dngos grub ma lus pa //
NK010(tha)004:2379: dam tshig nyid la brten gyur kyang //
NK010(tha)004:2380: rmongs dang ma rig nyon mongs pas //
NK010(tha)004:2381: zil gyis non pa bdag cag ni //
NK010(tha)004:2382: nyes pa du ma'i snod lags te //
NK010(tha)004:2383: mgon po thugs rje che rnams kyis //
NK010(tha)004:2384: thugs la khro bo mi mnga' yang //
NK010(tha)004:2385: legs nyes stangs 'dzin bdag po rnams //
NK010(tha)004:2386: skyon mthong tsam nas chad pa gcod //
NK010(tha)004:2387: 'gal zhing nongs pa ci mchis pa //
NK010(tha)004:2388: mthol lo bshags so tshangs par stsol //
NK010(tha)004:2389: yi ge brgya pa lan gsum gyis snying nas bshags par bya'o //
NK010(tha)004:2392: snod bcud lha dang gzhal yas su //
NK010(tha)004:2393: shar ba dag pa'i snod bcud kyang //
NK010(tha)004:2394: rten nyid brten pa lha rnams kyang //
NK010(tha)004:2395: gtso bo la thim de yang h'u //
NK010(tha)004:2396: zhabs kyu nas bzung n+aa da'i bar //
NK010(tha)004:2397: rim yal gdod ma'i gshis su a //
NK010(tha)004:2399: spyod lam gyi rnal 'byor du ldang ba ni /
NK010(tha)004:2400: slar yang rig pa byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)004:2401: rjes thob gnyug ma'i he ru ka /
NK010(tha)004:2402: phyag rgya gcig pa'i gnas gsum du //
NK010(tha)004:2403: yi ges mtshan pas rnam rtog bsrung //
NK010(tha)004:2404: badz+ra rak+sha hamh zhes rdo rje'i go bgo zhing /
NK010(tha)004:2405: yi ge brgya pas brtan par bya'o //
NK010(tha)004:2408: snang grags rig pa dkyil 'khor gsum gyi ngang //
NK010(tha)004:2409: bsod nams ye shes rim gnyis rnal 'byor tshogs //
NK010(tha)004:2410: mi gnas ye shes mya ngan 'das par bsngo //
NK010(tha)004:2411: kun kyang dpa' chen go 'phang thob par shog /
NK010(tha)004:2415: gdod ma'i mgon po rigs lnga gangs chen mtsho //
NK010(tha)004:2416: sku lnga lhun rdzogs sprul pa'i zhing khams la //
NK010(tha)004:2417: bskal bzang sangs rgyas stong rtsa byon pa yi //
NK010(tha)004:2418: sgron ma'i bskal pa bzang po'i bkra shis shog /
NK010(tha)004:2419: stong gsum mi mjed rdo rje theg pa'i zhing //
NK010(tha)004:2420: 'phur 'gro'i bstan pa 'byung gnas u rgyan yul //
NK010(tha)004:2421: gangs ri'i khrod du 'bod pa khri srong rje'i //
NK010(tha)004:2422: thugs bskyed bstan pa mtha' rgyas bkra shis shog /
NK010(tha)004:2423: 'dzam gling sa yi lte ba rdo rje gdan //
NK010(tha)004:2424: pan grub chos rgyal 'dzom pa chos 'khor gsum //
NK010(tha)004:2425: mdo sngags bstan pa dar ba gangs can ljongs //
NK010(tha)004:2426: rgyal bstan yun du gnas pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK010(tha)004:2427: chos skyong rgyal po tshangs pa'i me tog gis //
NK010(tha)004:2428: lo pan spyan drangs dka' bas btsa' ba'i rgyud //
NK010(tha)004:2429: ci gar dor nas rang bzo'i sngags rgyud kyis //
NK010(tha)004:2430: gangs ri'i khrod 'di skal ba ngan par byas //
NK010(tha)004:2431: rgyud las lung dang lung las man ngag tu //
NK010(tha)004:2432: sdebs nas sgrub thabs phrin las ston pa 'di //
NK010(tha)004:2433: o rgyan mkhan po'i bzhed gzhung ma nor phyin //
NK010(tha)004:2434: lung bstan dus babs bstan pa 'ba' zhig bsam //
NK010(tha)004:2435: gsang sngags rang gar blangs dang cis mtshungs rgyal rigs gang zag snyan brgyud kyi //
NK010(tha)004:2436: dbang dang byin rlabs chu rgyun ma nyams de yang rnams par rig pa tsam //
NK010(tha)004:2437: ngo bo gnyis med ye grol chen por chos nyid phur bu'i dbang thob pa'i //
NK010(tha)004:2438: byin rlabs lkog tu ma gyur yid ches 'di la nyams len mdzod dang gsal //
NK010(tha)004:2439: da lta chos kyi byin rlabs ma nyams kyang //
NK010(tha)004:2440: bsod nams snyigs mar 'gyur pa'i log shes kyis //
NK010(tha)004:2441: sngags kyi dngos grub bzung bar mi nus dus //
NK010(tha)004:2442: las can gcig srid de yis 'dzin par shog /
NK010(tha)004:2443: ces pa'ang rig 'dzin gyi slob dpon pad+ma sam+b+ha was
NK010(tha)004:2444: byin gyis brlabs pa'i rdzogs chen pa rang byung rdo
